{"type":"message","id":"7cfe8b5d","parentId":"33e774e1","timestamp":"2026-04-15T12:24:05.573Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_sgca1rqfy3o2_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"servers\": {\n    \"gitlab\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\n        \"-y\",\n        \"@openclaw/mcp-gitlab\"\n      ],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"GITLAB_URL\": \"https://gitlab.com\",\n        \"GITLAB_TOKEN\": \"YOUR_GITLAB_TOKEN\"\n      }\n    },\n    \"stitch\": {\n      \"command\": \"node\",\n      \"args\": [\n        \"/path/to/your/openclaw/mcp-stitch-key/server.mjs\"\n      ]\n    },\n    \"confluence\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\n        \"-y\",\n        \"confluence-mcp-server\"\n      ],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"CONFLUENCE_BASE_URL\": \"https://annoinfo.atlassian.net/wiki\",\n        \"CONFLUENCE_API_TOKEN\": \"YOUR_CONFLUENCE_TOKEN\",\n        \"CONFLUENCE_EMAIL\": \"your@email.com\"\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"list\": [\n    \"gitlab\",\n    \"confluence\",\n    \"stitch\"\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":152,"aggregated":"{\n  \"servers\": {\n    \"gitlab\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\n        \"-y\",\n        \"@openclaw/mcp-gitlab\"\n      ],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"GITLAB_URL\": \"https://gitlab.com\",\n        \"GITLAB_TOKEN\": \"YOUR_GITLAB_TOKEN\"\n      }\n    },\n    \"stitch\": {\n      \"command\": \"node\",\n      \"args\": [\n        \"/path/to/your/openclaw/mcp-stitch-key/server.mjs\"\n      ]\n    },\n    \"confluence\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\n        \"-y\",\n        \"confluence-mcp-server\"\n      ],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"CONFLUENCE_BASE_URL\": \"https://annoinfo.atlassian.net/wiki\",\n        \"CONFLUENCE_API_TOKEN\": \"YOUR_CONFLUENCE_TOKEN\",\n        \"CONFLUENCE_EMAIL\": \"your@email.com\"\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"list\": [\n    \"gitlab\",\n    \"confluence\",\n    \"stitch\"\n  ]\n}","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776255845528}}
{"type":"message","id":"2e1cb3a1","parentId":"7cfe8b5d","timestamp":"2026-04-15T12:24:13.624Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the issue. The user is saying that when they set up a new user in openclaw-tui, they enter their Confluence API key, email, API token, and bot token, but when they go to use it, the system still shows the Lead's (ninhkhuongpl7@gmail.com) Confluence data instead of the new user's data.\n\nThe problem is clear: The Confluence MCP credentials are **hardcoded in `openclaw.json`** with the Lead's credentials:\n- `CONF_USERNAME`: `ninhkhuongpl7@gmail.com`\n- `CONF_TOKEN`: Lead's API token\n- `CONF_BASE_URL`: `https://dtlx.atlassian.net/wiki`\n\n\n- These credentials are static in the config file and don't update when a new user sets up their own account, so the MCP keeps using the Lead's Confluence data instead of the new user's credentials.\n\nThe issue is that the openclaw-tui setup form doesn't actually persist the new user's credentials to the openclaw.json file, or the file is read-only so changes can't be saved. I should check whether the setup scripts are properly writing these credentials and whether there's a permissions issue preventing the write operation. The real issue is that when a new user enters their credentials in the openclaw-tui setup, those values aren't actually being saved to the openclaw.json file where the MCP servers read them from. The setup form likely validates the input but doesn't persist it, or there's a disconnect between where the form stores the data and where the MCP servers expect to find it.","thinkingSignature":"5637e8dcf09170a7b02c76baa1e303540a3a94eb4854f2664d7340c7ec13ffb3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_td0ntreupse2_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup/scripts/*.js /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup/scripts/*.sh 2>/dev/null | head -200"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_td0ntreupse2_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup/agent-defs/ 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1178,"output":450,"cacheRead":24321,"cacheWrite":1187,"totalTokens":27136,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776255845575,"responseId":"062eb6663ddbabb0c79003affea357e2"}}
{"type":"message","id":"437ea9fe","parentId":"2e1cb3a1","timestamp":"2026-04-15T12:24:13.872Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_td0ntreupse2_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env bash\n# =============================================================================\n# AHV OpenClaw Setup — ONE COMMAND INSTALL\n# =============================================================================\n# Usage:\n#   curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/maiychrus25/setup-openclaw/main/install.sh | bash\n#   ./install.sh dev\n# =============================================================================\n\nset -e\n\nREPO=\"https://github.com/maiychrus25/setup-openclaw.git\"\nINSTALL_DIR=\"${HOME}/.openclaw-setup\"\n\nRED='\\033[0;31m'; GREEN='\\033[0;32m'; YELLOW='\\033[1;33m'\nCYAN='\\033[0;36m'; BOLD='\\033[1m'; DIM='\\033[2m'; RESET='\\033[0m'\n\nlog()  { echo -e \"${GREEN}  ✅ $*${RESET}\"; }\nwarn() { echo -e \"${YELLOW}  ⚠️  $*${RESET}\"; }\ninfo() { echo -e \"${DIM}  • $*${RESET}\"; }\nstep() { echo -e \"${CYAN}  ▶ $*${RESET}\"; }\nerr()  { echo -e \"${RED}  ❌ $*${RESET}\" >&2; }\n\nheader() {\n  echo \"\"\n  echo -e \"${BOLD}╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗${RESET}\"\n  echo -e \"${BOLD}║     AHV OpenClaw Setup — ONE COMMAND INSTALL          ║${RESET}\"\n  echo -e \"${BOLD}╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝${RESET}\"\n  echo \"\"\n}\n\nneed() {\n  if ! command -v \"$1\" &>/dev/null; then\n    err \"Missing required: $1 — install first: $2\"\n    exit 1\n  fi\n}\n\nmain() {\n  header\n\n  # Check prerequisites\n  step \"Kiểm tra prerequisites...\"\n  need node \"https://nodejs.org\"\n  info \"Node.js: $(node --version)\"\n  info \"npm: $(npm --version)\"\n  log \"Prerequisites OK\"\n\n  # Check AHV API Key\n  if [ -z \"$AHVHOLDING_API_KEY\" ]; then\n    echo \"\"\n    warn \"Chua co AHV API Key!\"\n    echo \"\"\n    echo \"  1. Chay lenh nay de lay API key:\"\n    echo \"     curl -fsSL https://auto.ahvchat.com/setup.sh | bash\"\n    echo \"\"\n    echo \"  2. Sau do set bien moi truong:\"\n    echo \"     export AHVHOLDING_API_KEY=\\\"key_cua_ban\\\"\"\n    echo \"\"\n    echo \"  3. Chay lai setup nay\"\n    echo \"\"\n    exit 1\n  fi\n  info \"AHV API Key: ${AHVHOLDING_API_KEY:0:8}...\"\n\n  # Clone or update repo\n  step \"Tai AHV OpenClaw Setup...\"\n  if [ -d \"$INSTALL_DIR/.git\" ]; then\n    info \"Repo da co — pulling latest...\"\n    cd \"$INSTALL_DIR\" && git pull origin main --quiet\n  else\n    git clone --quiet \"$REPO\" \"$INSTALL_DIR\"\n    cd \"$INSTALL_DIR\"\n  fi\n  log \"Repo ready: $INSTALL_DIR\"\n\n  # npm install\n  step \"Cai dependencies...\"\n  npm install --silent 2>/dev/null || npm install\n  log \"Dependencies installed\"\n\n  # Run setup\n  local team=\"${1:-dev}\"\n  step \"Chay setup cho team: $team...\"\n  node bin/ahv-setup.js --team \"$team\"\n\n  # Done\n  local cfg=\"${HOME}/.openclaw/openclaw.json\"\n  echo \"\"\n  log \"Setup hoan tat!\"\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"  Tiếp theo:\"\n  echo \"  ${CYAN}1.${RESET} Restart gateway:\"\n  echo \"     openclaw gateway restart\"\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"  ${CYAN}2.${RESET} Mo TUI:\"\n  echo \"     openclaw tui --token \\$(grep token $cfg | head -1 | sed 's/.*\\\"\\([a-f0-9]*\\)\\\".*/\\1/')\"\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"  ${CYAN}3.${RESET} Kiem tra:\"\n  echo \"     openclaw agents list\"\n  echo \"\"\n}\n\nmain \"$@\"\n#!/usr/bin/env bash\n# =============================================================================\n# AHV OpenClaw Setup — ONE COMMAND INSTALL\n# =============================================================================\n# Usage:\n#   curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/maiychrus25/setup-openclaw/main/install.sh | bash\n#   ./install.sh dev\n# =============================================================================\n\nset -e\n\nREPO=\"https://github.com/maiychrus25/setup-openclaw.git\"\nINSTALL_DIR=\"${HOME}/.openclaw-setup\"\n\nRED='\\033[0;31m'; GREEN='\\033[0;32m'; YELLOW='\\033[1;33m'\nCYAN='\\033[0;36m'; BOLD='\\033[1m'; DIM='\\033[2m'; RESET='\\033[0m'\n\nlog()  { echo -e \"${GREEN}  ✅ $*${RESET}\"; }\nwarn() { echo -e \"${YELLOW}  ⚠️  $*${RESET}\"; }\ninfo() { echo -e \"${DIM}  • $*${RESET}\"; }\nstep() { echo -e \"${CYAN}  ▶ $*${RESET}\"; }\nerr()  { echo -e \"${RED}  ❌ $*${RESET}\" >&2; }\n\nheader() {\n  echo \"\"\n  echo -e \"${BOLD}╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗${RESET}\"\n  echo -e \"${BOLD}║     AHV OpenClaw Setup — ONE COMMAND INSTALL          ║${RESET}\"\n  echo -e \"${BOLD}╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝${RESET}\"\n  echo \"\"\n}\n\nneed() {\n  if ! command -v \"$1\" &>/dev/null; then\n    err \"Missing required: $1 — install first: $2\"\n    exit 1\n  fi\n}\n\nmain() {\n  header\n\n  # Check prerequisites\n  step \"Kiểm tra prerequisites...\"\n  need node \"https://nodejs.org\"\n  info \"Node.js: $(node --version)\"\n  info \"npm: $(npm --version)\"\n  log \"Prerequisites OK\"\n\n  # Check AHV API Key\n  if [ -z \"$AHVHOLDING_API_KEY\" ]; then\n    echo \"\"\n    warn \"Chua co AHV API Key!\"\n    echo \"\"\n    echo \"  1. Chay lenh nay de lay API key:\"\n    echo \"     curl -fsSL https://auto.ahvchat.com/setup.sh | bash\"\n    echo \"\"\n    echo \"  2. Sau do set bien moi truong:\"\n    echo \"     export AHVHOLDING_API_KEY=\\\"key_cua_ban\\\"\"\n    echo \"\"\n    echo \"  3. Chay lai setup nay\"\n    echo \"\"\n    exit 1\n  fi\n  info \"AHV API Key: ${AHVHOLDING_API_KEY:0:8}...\"\n\n  # Clone or update repo\n  step \"Tai AHV OpenClaw Setup...\"\n  if [ -d \"$INSTALL_DIR/.git\" ]; then\n    info \"Repo da co — pulling latest...\"\n    cd \"$INSTALL_DIR\" && git pull origin main --quiet\n  else\n    git clone --quiet \"$REPO\" \"$INSTALL_DIR\"\n    cd \"$INSTALL_DIR\"\n  fi\n  log \"Repo ready: $INSTALL_DIR\"\n\n  # npm install\n  step \"Cai dependencies...\"\n  npm install --silent 2>/dev/null || npm install\n  log \"Dependencies installed\"\n\n  # Run setup\n  local team=\"${1:-dev}\"\n  step \"Chay setup cho team: $team...\"\n  node bin/ahv-setup.js --team \"$team\"\n\n  # Done\n  local cfg=\"${HOME}/.openclaw/openclaw.json\"\n  echo \"\"\n  log \"Setup hoan tat!\"\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"  Tiếp theo:\"\n  echo \"  ${CYAN}1.${RESET} Restart gateway:\"\n  echo \"     openclaw gateway restart\"\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"  ${CYAN}2.${RESET} Mo TUI:\""}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":119,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env bash\n# =============================================================================\n# AHV OpenClaw Setup — ONE COMMAND INSTALL\n# =============================================================================\n# Usage:\n#   curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/maiychrus25/setup-openclaw/main/install.sh | bash\n#   ./install.sh dev\n# =============================================================================\n\nset -e\n\nREPO=\"https://github.com/maiychrus25/setup-openclaw.git\"\nINSTALL_DIR=\"${HOME}/.openclaw-setup\"\n\nRED='\\033[0;31m'; GREEN='\\033[0;32m'; YELLOW='\\033[1;33m'\nCYAN='\\033[0;36m'; BOLD='\\033[1m'; DIM='\\033[2m'; RESET='\\033[0m'\n\nlog()  { echo -e \"${GREEN}  ✅ $*${RESET}\"; }\nwarn() { echo -e \"${YELLOW}  ⚠️  $*${RESET}\"; }\ninfo() { echo -e \"${DIM}  • $*${RESET}\"; }\nstep() { echo -e \"${CYAN}  ▶ $*${RESET}\"; }\nerr()  { echo -e \"${RED}  ❌ $*${RESET}\" >&2; }\n\nheader() {\n  echo \"\"\n  echo -e \"${BOLD}╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗${RESET}\"\n  echo -e \"${BOLD}║     AHV OpenClaw Setup — ONE COMMAND INSTALL          ║${RESET}\"\n  echo -e \"${BOLD}╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝${RESET}\"\n  echo \"\"\n}\n\nneed() {\n  if ! command -v \"$1\" &>/dev/null; then\n    err \"Missing required: $1 — install first: $2\"\n    exit 1\n  fi\n}\n\nmain() {\n  header\n\n  # Check prerequisites\n  step \"Kiểm tra prerequisites...\"\n  need node \"https://nodejs.org\"\n  info \"Node.js: $(node --version)\"\n  info \"npm: $(npm --version)\"\n  log \"Prerequisites OK\"\n\n  # Check AHV API Key\n  if [ -z \"$AHVHOLDING_API_KEY\" ]; then\n    echo \"\"\n    warn \"Chua co AHV API Key!\"\n    echo \"\"\n    echo \"  1. Chay lenh nay de lay API key:\"\n    echo \"     curl -fsSL https://auto.ahvchat.com/setup.sh | bash\"\n    echo \"\"\n    echo \"  2. Sau do set bien moi truong:\"\n    echo \"     export AHVHOLDING_API_KEY=\\\"key_cua_ban\\\"\"\n    echo \"\"\n    echo \"  3. Chay lai setup nay\"\n    echo \"\"\n    exit 1\n  fi\n  info \"AHV API Key: ${AHVHOLDING_API_KEY:0:8}...\"\n\n  # Clone or update repo\n  step \"Tai AHV OpenClaw Setup...\"\n  if [ -d \"$INSTALL_DIR/.git\" ]; then\n    info \"Repo da co — pulling latest...\"\n    cd \"$INSTALL_DIR\" && git pull origin main --quiet\n  else\n    git clone --quiet \"$REPO\" \"$INSTALL_DIR\"\n    cd \"$INSTALL_DIR\"\n  fi\n  log \"Repo ready: $INSTALL_DIR\"\n\n  # npm install\n  step \"Cai dependencies...\"\n  npm install --silent 2>/dev/null || npm install\n  log \"Dependencies installed\"\n\n  # Run setup\n  local team=\"${1:-dev}\"\n  step \"Chay setup cho team: $team...\"\n  node bin/ahv-setup.js --team \"$team\"\n\n  # Done\n  local cfg=\"${HOME}/.openclaw/openclaw.json\"\n  echo \"\"\n  log \"Setup hoan tat!\"\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"  Tiếp theo:\"\n  echo \"  ${CYAN}1.${RESET} Restart gateway:\"\n  echo \"     openclaw gateway restart\"\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"  ${CYAN}2.${RESET} Mo TUI:\"\n  echo \"     openclaw tui --token \\$(grep token $cfg | head -1 | sed 's/.*\\\"\\([a-f0-9]*\\)\\\".*/\\1/')\"\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"  ${CYAN}3.${RESET} Kiem tra:\"\n  echo \"     openclaw agents list\"\n  echo \"\"\n}\n\nmain \"$@\"\n#!/usr/bin/env bash\n# =============================================================================\n# AHV OpenClaw Setup — ONE COMMAND INSTALL\n# =============================================================================\n# Usage:\n#   curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/maiychrus25/setup-openclaw/main/install.sh | bash\n#   ./install.sh dev\n# =============================================================================\n\nset -e\n\nREPO=\"https://github.com/maiychrus25/setup-openclaw.git\"\nINSTALL_DIR=\"${HOME}/.openclaw-setup\"\n\nRED='\\033[0;31m'; GREEN='\\033[0;32m'; YELLOW='\\033[1;33m'\nCYAN='\\033[0;36m'; BOLD='\\033[1m'; DIM='\\033[2m'; RESET='\\033[0m'\n\nlog()  { echo -e \"${GREEN}  ✅ $*${RESET}\"; }\nwarn() { echo -e \"${YELLOW}  ⚠️  $*${RESET}\"; }\ninfo() { echo -e \"${DIM}  • $*${RESET}\"; }\nstep() { echo -e \"${CYAN}  ▶ $*${RESET}\"; }\nerr()  { echo -e \"${RED}  ❌ $*${RESET}\" >&2; }\n\nheader() {\n  echo \"\"\n  echo -e \"${BOLD}╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗${RESET}\"\n  echo -e \"${BOLD}║     AHV OpenClaw Setup — ONE COMMAND INSTALL          ║${RESET}\"\n  echo -e \"${BOLD}╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝${RESET}\"\n  echo \"\"\n}\n\nneed() {\n  if ! command -v \"$1\" &>/dev/null; then\n    err \"Missing required: $1 — install first: $2\"\n    exit 1\n  fi\n}\n\nmain() {\n  header\n\n  # Check prerequisites\n  step \"Kiểm tra prerequisites...\"\n  need node \"https://nodejs.org\"\n  info \"Node.js: $(node --version)\"\n  info \"npm: $(npm --version)\"\n  log \"Prerequisites OK\"\n\n  # Check AHV API Key\n  if [ -z \"$AHVHOLDING_API_KEY\" ]; then\n    echo \"\"\n    warn \"Chua co AHV API Key!\"\n    echo \"\"\n    echo \"  1. Chay lenh nay de lay API key:\"\n    echo \"     curl -fsSL https://auto.ahvchat.com/setup.sh | bash\"\n    echo \"\"\n    echo \"  2. Sau do set bien moi truong:\"\n    echo \"     export AHVHOLDING_API_KEY=\\\"key_cua_ban\\\"\"\n    echo \"\"\n    echo \"  3. Chay lai setup nay\"\n    echo \"\"\n    exit 1\n  fi\n  info \"AHV API Key: ${AHVHOLDING_API_KEY:0:8}...\"\n\n  # Clone or update repo\n  step \"Tai AHV OpenClaw Setup...\"\n  if [ -d \"$INSTALL_DIR/.git\" ]; then\n    info \"Repo da co — pulling latest...\"\n    cd \"$INSTALL_DIR\" && git pull origin main --quiet\n  else\n    git clone --quiet \"$REPO\" \"$INSTALL_DIR\"\n    cd \"$INSTALL_DIR\"\n  fi\n  log \"Repo ready: $INSTALL_DIR\"\n\n  # npm install\n  step \"Cai dependencies...\"\n  npm install --silent 2>/dev/null || npm install\n  log \"Dependencies installed\"\n\n  # Run setup\n  local team=\"${1:-dev}\"\n  step \"Chay setup cho team: $team...\"\n  node bin/ahv-setup.js --team \"$team\"\n\n  # Done\n  local cfg=\"${HOME}/.openclaw/openclaw.json\"\n  echo \"\"\n  log \"Setup hoan tat!\"\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"  Tiếp theo:\"\n  echo \"  ${CYAN}1.${RESET} Restart gateway:\"\n  echo \"     openclaw gateway restart\"\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"  ${CYAN}2.${RESET} Mo TUI:\"","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776255853830}}
