{"type":"message","id":"64807308","parentId":"6ce4a4aa","timestamp":"2026-04-15T12:24:24.421Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me check the actual setup script that handles the credentials:","thinkingSignature":"20ffee50ac043c8d6c11d67375c05951fa4e1625c8492a6d3a6756df7e4155ea"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cs7ylv7jt8ln_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup/bin/ahv-setup.js 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":2096,"output":70,"cacheRead":25151,"cacheWrite":1860,"totalTokens":29177,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776255853917,"responseId":"062eb66ff663a7b01ef36adb4a55d38e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"72894118","parentId":"64807308","timestamp":"2026-04-15T12:24:24.645Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_cs7ylv7jt8ln_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env node\n\"use strict\";\n\nconst fs = require(\"fs\");\nconst path = require(\"path\");\nconst { execSync } = require(\"child_process\");\nconst inquirer = require(\"inquirer\");\nconst chalk = require(\"chalk\");\nconst shell = require(\"shelljs\");\nconst zlib = require(\"zlib\");\nconst PKG_DIR = path.join(__dirname, \"..\");\n\n// ─── Unpack skills ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n// ─── Inline unpack skills (no execSync to avoid timeout) ─────────────────\nfunction unpackSkills(skillsPackPath, destDir) {\n  if (!fs.existsSync(skillsPackPath)) {\n    console.log(chalk.yellow(`  ⚠️  skills-full.pack not found — skipping skills`));\n    return;\n  }\n  try {\n    const zlib = require(\"zlib\");\n    const SKILL_KEY = \"ahv-openclaw-2026\";\n    const pack = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(skillsPackPath, \"utf8\"));\n    let count = 0;\n    for (const entry of pack.manifest) {\n      const buf = Buffer.from(pack.payloads[entry.file], \"base64\");\n      const kb = Buffer.from(SKILL_KEY, \"utf8\");\n      const dec = Buffer.alloc(buf.length);\n      for (let i = 0; i < buf.length; i++) dec[i] = buf[i] ^ kb[i % kb.length] ^ (i & 0xff);\n      const content = zlib.inflateSync(dec);\n\n      // File path: skills/senior-backend/SKILL.md OR skills/senior-backend/references/...\n      const filePath = path.join(destDir, \"skills\", entry.file);\n      fs.mkdirSync(path.dirname(filePath), { recursive: true });\n      fs.writeFileSync(filePath, content);\n\n      // chmod 500 only on SKILL.md, 444 on supporting files\n      if (entry.file.endsWith(\"SKILL.md\")) {\n        fs.chmodSync(filePath, 0o500);\n      } else {\n        fs.chmodSync(filePath, 0o444);\n      }\n      count++;\n    }\n    const skillCount = pack.manifest.filter(e => e.file.endsWith(\"SKILL.md\")).length;\n    const refCount = pack.manifest.length - skillCount;\n    console.log(chalk.dim(`  📦 ${skillCount} skills + ${refCount} refs/scripts/templates unpacked`));\n  } catch (err) {\n    console.log(chalk.yellow(`  ⚠️  Unpack failed: ${err.message}`));\n  }\n}\n\n// ─── Banner ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nconst BANNER = `\n╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\n║   AHV OpenClaw Setup — Team Onboarding v1.0       ║\n║   Tự động cài đặt agents + config cho team       ║\n╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\n`;\n\n// ─── Team definitions ────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nconst TEAMS = {\n  dev: {\n    name: \"👨💻 Team Dev\",\n    desc: \"Backend, Frontend, DevOps, Architecture\",\n    agents: [\n      \"senior-backend\", \"senior-frontend\", \"senior-architect\",\n      \"senior-devops\", \"typescript-reviewer\", \"shadcn-expert\",\n      \"clean-code\", \"coding-standards\", \"refactor-cleaner\",\n      \"realistic-seeder\", \"planner\", \"prompt-optimizer\"\n    ],\n    mcp: [\"gitlab\", \"confluence\", \"stitch\"]\n  },\n  ba: {\n    name: \"📊 Team BA\",\n    desc: \"Product Owner, Strategy, Epic Design\",\n    agents: [\n      \"agile-product-owner\", \"product-strategy\", \"market-intelligence\",\n      \"content-strategy\", \"product-marketing-context\",\n      \"epic-design\", \"planner\"\n    ],\n    mcp: [\"confluence\"]\n  },\n  qa: {\n    name: \"🧪 Team QA\",\n    desc: \"QA, Playwright, Security, Performance\",\n    agents: [\n      \"senior-qa\", \"playwright-pro\", \"code-reviewer\",\n      \"security-reviewer\", \"performance-optimizer\", \"planner\"\n    ],\n    mcp: [\"gitlab\", \"confluence-dtlx\", \"confluence-qlhv\"]\n  }\n};\n\n// ─── Required credentials per team ──────────────────────────────────────\nconst REQUIRED_CREDS = {\n  dev:  [\"AHV_API_KEY\", \"GITLAB_TOKEN\", \"CONF_TOKEN\", \"STITCH_API_KEY\", \"TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN\"],\n  ba:   [\"AHV_API_KEY\", \"CONF_TOKEN\", \"TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN\"],\n  qa:   [\"AHV_API_KEY\", \"GITLAB_TOKEN\", \"CONF_TOKEN\", \"TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN\"]\n};\n\n// ─── Config template path ───────────────────────────────────────────────\nfunction getConfigPath(team) {\n  return path.join(__dirname, \"..\", \"configs\", `team-${team}.json`);\n}\n\nfunction getOpenclawPath(customPath) {\n  if (customPath) {\n    const resolved = customPath.replace(/^\\$HOME/, process.env.HOME || \"\");\n    return path.join(resolved, \"openclaw.json\");\n  }\n  const home = process.env.HOME || process.env.USERPROFILE;\n  return path.join(home, \".openclaw\", \"openclaw.json\");\n}\n\nfunction getWorkspacePath(customPath) {\n  if (customPath) {\n    const resolved = customPath.replace(/^\\$HOME/, process.env.HOME || \"\");\n    return path.join(resolved, \"workspace\");\n  }\n  const home = process.env.HOME || process.env.USERPROFILE;\n  return path.join(home, \".openclaw\", \"workspace\");\n}\n\n// ─── Check prerequisites ────────────────────────────────────────────────\nfunction checkPrereqs() {\n  console.log(chalk.dim(\"\\n🔍 Kiểm tra prerequisites...\\n\"));\n\n  const checks = [\n    { cmd: \"node --version\", name: \"Node.js\" },\n    { cmd: \"npm --version\", name: \"npm\" }\n  ];\n\n  let allOk = true;\n  for (const check of checks) {\n    try {\n      const out = execSync(check.cmd, { encoding: \"utf8\", timeout: 5000 }).trim();\n      console.log(`  ${chalk.green(\"✅\")} ${check.name}: ${out}`);\n    } catch {\n      console.log(`  ${chalk.red(\"❌\")} ${check.name}: chưa cài đặt`);\n      allOk = false;\n    }\n  }\n\n  if (!allOk) {\n    console.log(chalk.red(\"\\n❌ Vui lòng cài đặt Node.js trước: https://nodejs.org/\\n\"));\n    process.exit(1);\n  }\n\n  try {\n    execSync(\"openclaw --version\", { encoding: \"utf8\", timeout: 5000 });\n    console.log(`  ${chalk.green(\"✅\")} OpenClaw CLI: đã cài`);\n  } catch {\n    console.log(chalk.yellow(\"  ⚠️  OpenClaw CLI: chưa cài (sẽ cài sau)\"));\n    try {\n      execSync(\"npm install -g openclaw\", { encoding: \"utf8\", timeout: 60000 });\n      console.log(`  ${chalk.green(\"✅\")} OpenClaw CLI: đã cài đặt`);\n    } catch {\n      console.log(chalk.red(\"  ❌ Cài OpenClaw thất bại. Chạy: npm install -g openclaw\"));\n    }\n  }\n}\n\n// ─── Load team config template ─────────────────────────────────────────\nfunction loadTemplate(team) {\n  const configPath = getConfigPath(team);\n  if (!fs.existsSync(configPath)) {\n    console.log(chalk.red(`\\n❌ Config không tìm thấy: ${configPath}`));\n    process.exit(1);\n  }\n  return JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(configPath, \"utf8\"));\n}\n\n// ─── Collect credentials interactively ──────────────────────────────────\nasync function collectCredentials(team) {\n  const required = REQUIRED_CREDS[team];\n  const questions = [];\n\n  for (const cred of required) {\n    let message = \"\";\n    let name = \"\";\n    let validate = () => true;\n\n    switch (cred) {\n      case \"AHV_API_KEY\":\n        message = \"AHV API Key (từ https://auto.ahvchat.com → Account → API Keys)\";\n        name = \"ahvApiKey\";\n        validate = (v) => v.startsWith(\"sk-\") || \"Phải bắt đầu bằng sk-\";\n        break;\n      case \"GITLAB_TOKEN\":\n        message = \"GitLab Personal Access Token (https://gitlab.com → Settings → Access Tokens)\";\n        name = \"gitlabToken\";\n        validate = (v) => v.startsWith(\"glpat-\") || \"Phải bắt đầu bằng glpat-\";\n        break;\n      case \"CONF_TOKEN\":\n        questions.push({\n          type: \"input\",\n          name: \"confUrl\",\n          message: chalk.cyan(\"Confluence Base URL (VD: https://annoinfo.atlassian.net/wiki):\"),\n          default: \"https://annoinfo.atlassian.net/wiki\",\n          validate: (v) => v.startsWith(\"http\") || \"URL phải bắt đầu bằng http\"\n        });\n        questions.push({\n          type: \"input\",\n          name: \"confEmail\",\n          message: chalk.cyan(\"Confluence Email (email đăng nhập Atlassian):\"),\n          default: \"\",\n          validate: (v) => v.includes(\"@\") || \"Email không hợp lệ\"\n        });\n        questions.push({\n          type: \"input\",\n          name: \"confToken\",\n          message: chalk.cyan(\"Confluence API Token (https://id.atlassian.com → Security → API Tokens):\"),\n          default: \"\",\n          validate: (v) => v.length > 5 || \"Token không hợp lệ\"\n        });\n        continue;\n      case \"STITCH_API_KEY\":\n        message = \"Stitch API Key (https://stitch.design → Dashboard)\";\n        name = \"stitchKey\";\n        validate = (v) => v.length > 10 || \"Token không hợp lệ\";\n        break;\n      case \"TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN\":\n        message = \"Telegram Bot Token (từ @BotFather, format: 123456:ABC-DEF...)\";\n        name = \"telegramBot\";\n        validate = (v) => v.includes(\":\") || \"Bot token phải có dạng xxx:yyy\";\n        break;\n    }\n\n    questions.push({\n      type: \"input\",\n      name,\n      message: chalk.cyan(`${cred}:`),\n      default: \"\",\n      validate\n    });\n  }\n\n  const pathQuestions = [\n    {\n      type: \"input\",\n      name: \"openclawPath\",\n      message: chalk.cyan(\"openclaw home (ENTER = ~/.openclaw):\"),\n      default: \"$HOME/.openclaw\",\n      validate: (v) => v.length > 0 || \"Path không được trống\"\n    }\n  ];\n  return inquirer.prompt([...questions, ...pathQuestions]);\n}\n\n// ─── Inject credentials into config ────────────────────────────────────\nfunction applyCredentials(config, answers, team) {\n  // AHV API Key\n  config.env.AHVHOLDING_API_KEY = answers.ahvApiKey;\n  config.models.providers.ahvholding.apiKey = answers.ahvApiKey;\n\n  // GitLab Token\n  if (answers.gitlabToken) {\n    config.env.GITLAB_TOKEN = answers.gitlabToken;\n    const gitlab = config.mcp?.servers?.gitlab;\n    if (gitlab?.env) {\n      gitlab.env.GITLAB_URL = answers.gitlabUrl || 'https://gitlab.com';\n      gitlab.env.GITLAB_TOKEN = answers.gitlabToken;\n    }\n  }\n\n  // Confluence — mcp.servers (NOT mcpServers)\n  const mcpServers = config.mcp?.servers || {};\n  for (const key of Object.keys(mcpServers)) {\n    if (key === \"confluence\" && mcpServers[key].env) {\n      mcpServers[key].env.CONFLUENCE_API_TOKEN = answers.confToken;\n    }\n    if (key === \"stitch\" && mcpServers[key].env && answers.stitchKey) {\n      mcpServers[key].env.STITCH_API_KEY = answers.stitchKey;\n    }\n  }\n\n  // Telegram Bot — channels.telegram.bots (NOT accounts)\n  const botKeys = Object.keys(config.channels?.telegram?.bots || {});\n  for (const botKey of botKeys) {\n    if (config.channels.telegram.bots[botKey].botToken === \"YOUR_TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN\") {\n      config.channels.telegram.bots[botKey].botToken = answers.telegramBot;\n    }\n  }\n\n  return config;\n}\n\n// ─── Apply config to ~/.openclaw ────────────────────────────────────────\nfunction applyConfig(config, answers, team) {\n  const openclawPath = getOpenclawPath(answers.openclawPath);\n  const openclawDir = path.dirname(openclawPath);\n  const workspaceDir = getWorkspacePath(answers.openclawPath);\n\n  console.log(chalk.dim(\"\\n📁 Tạo thư mục...\\n\"));\n\n  // Create directories\n  const dirs = [openclawDir, workspaceDir];\n  for (const dir of dirs) {\n    if (!fs.existsSync(dir)) {\n      fs.mkdirSync(dir, { recursive: true });\n      console.log(`  ${chalk.green(\"📂\")} Tạo: ${dir}`);\n    }\n  }\n\n  // Backup existing config\n  if (fs.existsSync(openclawPath)) {\n    const backupPath = openclawPath + `.backup-${Date.now()}.json`;\n    fs.copyFileSync(openclawPath, backupPath);\n    console.log(`  ${chalk.yellow(\"💾\")} Backup: ${backupPath}`);\n  }\n\n  // Apply path substitutions using answers.openclawPath\n  const homePath = answers.openclawPath\n    ? answers.openclawPath.replace(/^\\$HOME/, process.env.HOME || \"\")\n    : (process.env.HOME || \"\") + \"/.openclaw\";\n\n  // Build final config from template (config already has credentials injected)\n  let finalConfig = JSON.parse(JSON.stringify(config));\n\n  // Fix default workspace\n  if (finalConfig.agents?.defaults?.workspace) {\n    finalConfig.agents.defaults.workspace = `${homePath}/workspace`;\n  }\n  // Fix per-agent workspaces and agentDirs\n  for (const agent of finalConfig.agents?.list || []) {\n    if (agent.workspace?.startsWith(\"/path/to/\")) {\n      agent.workspace = `${homePath}/workspaces/${agent.id}`;\n    }\n    if (agent.agentDir?.startsWith(\"/path/to/\")) {\n      agent.agentDir = `${homePath}/agents/${agent.id}/agent`;\n    }\n  }\n  // Fix MCP server paths — use mcp.servers\n  const mcpServers = finalConfig.mcp?.servers || {};\n  for (const key of Object.keys(mcpServers)) {\n    const srv = mcpServers[key];\n    if (srv.command === \"node\" && srv.args) {\n      for (let i = 0; i < srv.args.length; i++) {\n        if (srv.args[i].startsWith(\"/path/to/\")) {\n          srv.args[i] = `${homePath}/mcp-stitch-key/server.mjs`;\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n\n  fs.writeFileSync(openclawPath, JSON.stringify(finalConfig, null, 2), \"utf8\");\n  console.log(`  ${chalk.green(\"✅\")} Paths substituted: ${homePath}`);\n\n  // ─── Unpack encrypted skills ─────────────────────────────────────────────\n  // Skills go to ~/.openclaw/skills/{agent}/SKILL.md\n  const packPath = path.join(__dirname, \"..\", \"skills.pack\");\n  if (fs.existsSync(packPath)) {\n    unpackSkills(packPath, homePath);\n  } else {\n    console.log(chalk.yellow(`  ⚠️  skills.pack not found — skills skipped`));\n  }\n\n  // ─── Init agents (workspace + files) ─────────────────────────────────────────\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`\\n  🤖 Tạo ${TEAMS[team].agents.length} agent workspaces...\\n`));\n  for (const agentId of TEAMS[team].agents) {\n    const wsDir = path.join(homePath, \"workspaces\", agentId);\n    fs.mkdirSync(wsDir, { recursive: true });\n\n    const nameMap = {\n      \"senior-backend\":\"Senior Backend Engineer\",\"senior-frontend\":\"Senior Frontend Engineer\",\n      \"senior-architect\":\"Senior System Architect\",\"senior-devops\":\"Senior DevOps Engineer\",\n      \"senior-qa\":\"Senior QA Engineer\",\"senior-security\":\"Senior Security Engineer\",\n      \"typescript-reviewer\":\"TypeScript Reviewer\",\"shadcn-expert\":\"shadcn/ui Expert\",\n      \"clean-code\":\"Clean Code Specialist\",\"coding-standards\":\"Coding Standards Enforcer\",\n      \"refactor-cleaner\":\"Refactor Cleaner\",\"realistic-seeder\":\"Realistic Seeder\",\n      \"planner\":\"Planner Agent\",\"prompt-optimizer\":\"Prompt Optimizer\",\n      \"agile-product-owner\":\"Agile Product Owner\",\"product-strategy\":\"Product Strategist\",\n      \"market-intelligence\":\"Market Intelligence Agent\",\"content-strategy\":\"Content Strategist\",\n      \"product-marketing-context\":\"Product Marketing Agent\",\"epic-design\":\"Epic Designer\",\n      \"playwright-pro\":\"Playwright Pro\",\"code-reviewer\":\"Code Reviewer\",\n      \"security-reviewer\":\"Security Reviewer\",\"performance-optimizer\":\"Performance Optimizer\"\n    };\n    const displayName = nameMap[agentId] || agentId;\n\n    // Copy agent files from existing OpenClaw workspace on this machine\n    // Try multiple common locations\n    const searchPaths = [\n      path.join(process.env.OPENCLAW_HOME || \"\", \"workspaces2\", \"v4-ecosystem-review\", agentId),\n      path.join(process.env.HOME || \"\", \".openclaw\", \"workspaces2\", \"v4-ecosystem-review\", agentId),\n      path.join(process.env.HOME || \"\", \".openclaw\", \"workspaces\", agentId),\n    ];\n    const coreFiles = [\"SOUL.md\",\"IDENTITY.md\",\"AGENTS.md\",\"USER.md\",\n      \"BOOTSTRAP.md\",\"HEARTBEAT.md\",\"TOOLS.md\",\"MEMORY.md\",\n      \"SKILL_GATES.md\",\"DEV_GATE.md\"];\n\n    let copied = 0;\n    for (const srcDir of searchPaths) {\n      if (fs.existsSync(srcDir)) {\n        for (const file of coreFiles) {\n          const src = path.join(srcDir, file);\n          if (fs.existsSync(src)) {\n            fs.copyFileSync(src, path.join(wsDir, file));\n            copied++;\n          }\n        }\n        break; // stop at first found\n      }\n    }\n    if (copied === 0) {\n      console.log(chalk.yellow(`  ⚠️  No source agent files found for ${agentId} — skipping`));\n    }\n    console.log(chalk.dim(`  ✅ ${agentId}`));\n  }\n\n  return openclawPath;\n}\n\n// ─── Restart gateway ───────────────────────────────────────────────────\nfunction restartGateway() {\n  console.log(chalk.dim(\"\\n🔄 Restarting OpenClaw gateway...\\n\"));\n  try {\n    execSync(\"openclaw gateway restart\", { encoding: \"utf8\", timeout: 30000 });\n    console.log(`  ${chalk.green(\"✅\")} Gateway restarted`);\n  } catch (e) {\n    console.log(chalk.yellow(\"  ⚠️  Không restart được tự động. Chạy thủ công:\"));\n    console.log(chalk.cyan(\"    openclaw gateway restart\"));\n  }\n}\n\n// ─── Main ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nasync function main() {\n  console.log(BANNER);\n\n  // Parse args\n  const args = process.argv.slice(2);\n  let teamArg = null;\n  let skipIntro = false;\n\n  for (const arg of args) {\n    if (arg === \"--team\" || arg === \"-t\") {\n      const idx = args.indexOf(arg);\n      teamArg = args[idx + 1];\n    }\n    if (arg.startsWith(\"--team=\")) {\n      teamArg = arg.replace(\"--team=\", \"\");\n    }\n    if (arg === \"--yes\" || arg === \"-y\") skipIntro = true;\n  }\n\n  // Check prereqs\n  checkPrereqs();\n\n  // Select team\n  let team = teamArg;\n  if (!team) {\n    const { selected } = await inquirer.prompt([\n      {\n        type: \"list\",\n        name: \"selected\",\n        message: chalk.cyan(\"Chọn team của bạn:\"),\n        choices: [\n          { name: \"👨💻 Team Dev  — Backend, Frontend, DevOps, Architecture\", value: \"dev\" },\n          { name: \"📊 Team BA   — Product Owner, Strategy, Epic Design\", value: \"ba\" },\n          { name: \"🧪 Team QA  — QA, Playwright, Security, Performance\", value: \"qa\" }\n        ]\n      }\n    ]);\n    team = selected;\n  }\n\n  if (!TEAMS[team]) {\n    console.log(chalk.red(`\\n❌ Team không hợp lệ: ${team}`));\n    console.log(chalk.dim(\"Chọn: dev | ba | qa\\n\"));\n    process.exit(1);\n  }\n\n  console.log(chalk.bold(`\\n${chalk.cyan(\"▶\")} ${TEAMS[team].name}`));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`   ${TEAMS[team].desc}`));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`   Agents: ${TEAMS[team].agents.length}`));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`   MCP: ${TEAMS[team].mcp.join(\", \")}\\n`));\n\n  // Confirm\n  if (!skipIntro) {\n    const { confirm } = await inquirer.prompt([\n      {\n        type: \"confirm\",\n        name: \"confirm\",\n        message: chalk.cyan(\"Tiếp tục cài đặt?\"),\n        default: true\n      }\n    ]);\n    if (!confirm) {\n      console.log(chalk.dim(\"\\nĐã hủy.\\n\"));\n      process.exit(0);\n    }\n  }\n\n  // Load template\n  console.log(chalk.dim(\"📋 Load config template...\\n\"));\n  let config = loadTemplate(team);\n\n  // Collect credentials\n  console.log(chalk.bold(chalk.underline(\"\\n🔐 Nhập credentials (tự tạo cho team của bạn)\\n\")));\n  const answers = await collectCredentials(team);\n\n  // Apply\n  config = applyCredentials(config, answers, team);\n\n  // Summary\n  console.log(chalk.bold(\"\\n📦 Tổng kết config:\\n\"));\n  console.log(`  ${chalk.green(\"✓\")} Team: ${TEAMS[team].name}`);\n  console.log(`  ${chalk.green(\"✓\")} Agents: ${TEAMS[team].agents.join(\", \")}`);\n  console.log(`  ${chalk.green(\"✓\")} MCP: ${TEAMS[team].mcp.join(\", \")}`);\n\n  // Confirm before writing\n  const { write } = await inquirer.prompt([\n    {\n      type: \"confirm\",\n      name: \"write\",\n      message: chalk.cyan(\"\\nGhi config vào ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json?\"),\n      default: true\n    }\n  ]);\n\n  if (!write) {\n    console.log(chalk.dim(\"\\nĐã hủy. Config chưa được ghi.\\n\"));\n    process.exit(0);\n  }\n\n  const configPath = applyConfig(config, answers, team);\n  const homePath = answers.openclawPath\n    ? answers.openclawPath.replace(/^\\$HOME\\//, process.env.HOME || \"\")\n    : (process.env.HOME || \"\") + \"/.openclaw\";\n\n  // Restart gateway\n  restartGateway();\n\n  // Done\n  console.log(chalk.bold(chalk.green(\"\\n✅ Setup hoàn tất!\\n\")));\n  console.log(`  Config: ${configPath}`);\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`\\n  Đã làm:`));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`  • Credentials + config → ${configPath}`));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`  • Skills unpacked → ${homePath}/skills/`));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`  • ${TEAMS[team].agents.length} agent workspaces + files tạo`));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`  • Gateway restarted`));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`\\n  Kiểm tra: openclaw status`));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`  Xem agents: openclaw agents list`));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`  Gateway token: grep token ${configPath}`));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`  TUI: openclaw tui --token <token>`));\n\n}\n\nmain().catch((err) => {\n  console.error(chalk.red(\"\\n❌ Lỗi:\"), err.message);\n  process.exit(1);\n});"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":112,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env node\n\"use strict\";\n\nconst fs = require(\"fs\");\nconst path = require(\"path\");\nconst { execSync } = require(\"child_process\");\nconst inquirer = require(\"inquirer\");\nconst chalk = require(\"chalk\");\nconst shell = require(\"shelljs\");\nconst zlib = require(\"zlib\");\nconst PKG_DIR = path.join(__dirname, \"..\");\n\n// ─── Unpack skills ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n// ─── Inline unpack skills (no execSync to avoid timeout) ─────────────────\nfunction unpackSkills(skillsPackPath, destDir) {\n  if (!fs.existsSync(skillsPackPath)) {\n    console.log(chalk.yellow(`  ⚠️  skills-full.pack not found — skipping skills`));\n    return;\n  }\n  try {\n    const zlib = require(\"zlib\");\n    const SKILL_KEY = \"ahv-openclaw-2026\";\n    const pack = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(skillsPackPath, \"utf8\"));\n    let count = 0;\n    for (const entry of pack.manifest) {\n      const buf = Buffer.from(pack.payloads[entry.file], \"base64\");\n      const kb = Buffer.from(SKILL_KEY, \"utf8\");\n      const dec = Buffer.alloc(buf.length);\n      for (let i = 0; i < buf.length; i++) dec[i] = buf[i] ^ kb[i % kb.length] ^ (i & 0xff);\n      const content = zlib.inflateSync(dec);\n\n      // File path: skills/senior-backend/SKILL.md OR skills/senior-backend/references/...\n      const filePath = path.join(destDir, \"skills\", entry.file);\n      fs.mkdirSync(path.dirname(filePath), { recursive: true });\n      fs.writeFileSync(filePath, content);\n\n      // chmod 500 only on SKILL.md, 444 on supporting files\n      if (entry.file.endsWith(\"SKILL.md\")) {\n        fs.chmodSync(filePath, 0o500);\n      } else {\n        fs.chmodSync(filePath, 0o444);\n      }\n      count++;\n    }\n    const skillCount = pack.manifest.filter(e => e.file.endsWith(\"SKILL.md\")).length;\n    const refCount = pack.manifest.length - skillCount;\n    console.log(chalk.dim(`  📦 ${skillCount} skills + ${refCount} refs/scripts/templates unpacked`));\n  } catch (err) {\n    console.log(chalk.yellow(`  ⚠️  Unpack failed: ${err.message}`));\n  }\n}\n\n// ─── Banner ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nconst BANNER = `\n╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\n║   AHV OpenClaw Setup — Team Onboarding v1.0       ║\n║   Tự động cài đặt agents + config cho team       ║\n╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\n`;\n\n// ─── Team definitions ────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nconst TEAMS = {\n  dev: {\n    name: \"👨💻 Team Dev\",\n    desc: \"Backend, Frontend, DevOps, Architecture\",\n    agents: [\n      \"senior-backend\", \"senior-frontend\", \"senior-architect\",\n      \"senior-devops\", \"typescript-reviewer\", \"shadcn-expert\",\n      \"clean-code\", \"coding-standards\", \"refactor-cleaner\",\n      \"realistic-seeder\", \"planner\", \"prompt-optimizer\"\n    ],\n    mcp: [\"gitlab\", \"confluence\", \"stitch\"]\n  },\n  ba: {\n    name: \"📊 Team BA\",\n    desc: \"Product Owner, Strategy, Epic Design\",\n    agents: [\n      \"agile-product-owner\", \"product-strategy\", \"market-intelligence\",\n      \"content-strategy\", \"product-marketing-context\",\n      \"epic-design\", \"planner\"\n    ],\n    mcp: [\"confluence\"]\n  },\n  qa: {\n    name: \"🧪 Team QA\",\n    desc: \"QA, Playwright, Security, Performance\",\n    agents: [\n      \"senior-qa\", \"playwright-pro\", \"code-reviewer\",\n      \"security-reviewer\", \"performance-optimizer\", \"planner\"\n    ],\n    mcp: [\"gitlab\", \"confluence-dtlx\", \"confluence-qlhv\"]\n  }\n};\n\n// ─── Required credentials per team ──────────────────────────────────────\nconst REQUIRED_CREDS = {\n  dev:  [\"AHV_API_KEY\", \"GITLAB_TOKEN\", \"CONF_TOKEN\", \"STITCH_API_KEY\", \"TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN\"],\n  ba:   [\"AHV_API_KEY\", \"CONF_TOKEN\", \"TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN\"],\n  qa:   [\"AHV_API_KEY\", \"GITLAB_TOKEN\", \"CONF_TOKEN\", \"TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN\"]\n};\n\n// ─── Config template path ───────────────────────────────────────────────\nfunction getConfigPath(team) {\n  return path.join(__dirname, \"..\", \"configs\", `team-${team}.json`);\n}\n\nfunction getOpenclawPath(customPath) {\n  if (customPath) {\n    const resolved = customPath.replace(/^\\$HOME/, process.env.HOME || \"\");\n    return path.join(resolved, \"openclaw.json\");\n  }\n  const home = process.env.HOME || process.env.USERPROFILE;\n  return path.join(home, \".openclaw\", \"openclaw.json\");\n}\n\nfunction getWorkspacePath(customPath) {\n  if (customPath) {\n    const resolved = customPath.replace(/^\\$HOME/, process.env.HOME || \"\");\n    return path.join(resolved, \"workspace\");\n  }\n  const home = process.env.HOME || process.env.USERPROFILE;\n  return path.join(home, \".openclaw\", \"workspace\");\n}\n\n// ─── Check prerequisites ────────────────────────────────────────────────\nfunction checkPrereqs() {\n  console.log(chalk.dim(\"\\n🔍 Kiểm tra prerequisites...\\n\"));\n\n  const checks = [\n    { cmd: \"node --version\", name: \"Node.js\" },\n    { cmd: \"npm --version\", name: \"npm\" }\n  ];\n\n  let allOk = true;\n  for (const check of checks) {\n    try {\n      const out = execSync(check.cmd, { encoding: \"utf8\", timeout: 5000 }).trim();\n      console.log(`  ${chalk.green(\"✅\")} ${check.name}: ${out}`);\n    } catch {\n      console.log(`  ${chalk.red(\"❌\")} ${check.name}: chưa cài đặt`);\n      allOk = false;\n    }\n  }\n\n  if (!allOk) {\n    console.log(chalk.red(\"\\n❌ Vui lòng cài đặt Node.js trước: https://nodejs.org/\\n\"));\n    process.exit(1);\n  }\n\n  try {\n    execSync(\"openclaw --version\", { encoding: \"utf8\", timeout: 5000 });\n    console.log(`  ${chalk.green(\"✅\")} OpenClaw CLI: đã cài`);\n  } catch {\n    console.log(chalk.yellow(\"  ⚠️  OpenClaw CLI: chưa cài (sẽ cài sau)\"));\n    try {\n      execSync(\"npm install -g openclaw\", { encoding: \"utf8\", timeout: 60000 });\n      console.log(`  ${chalk.green(\"✅\")} OpenClaw CLI: đã cài đặt`);\n    } catch {\n      console.log(chalk.red(\"  ❌ Cài OpenClaw thất bại. Chạy: npm install -g openclaw\"));\n    }\n  }\n}\n\n// ─── Load team config template ─────────────────────────────────────────\nfunction loadTemplate(team) {\n  const configPath = getConfigPath(team);\n  if (!fs.existsSync(configPath)) {\n    console.log(chalk.red(`\\n❌ Config không tìm thấy: ${configPath}`));\n    process.exit(1);\n  }\n  return JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(configPath, \"utf8\"));\n}\n\n// ─── Collect credentials interactively ──────────────────────────────────\nasync function collectCredentials(team) {\n  const required = REQUIRED_CREDS[team];\n  const questions = [];\n\n  for (const cred of required) {\n    let message = \"\";\n    let name = \"\";\n    let validate = () => true;\n\n    switch (cred) {\n      case \"AHV_API_KEY\":\n        message = \"AHV API Key (từ https://auto.ahvchat.com → Account → API Keys)\";\n        name = \"ahvApiKey\";\n        validate = (v) => v.startsWith(\"sk-\") || \"Phải bắt đầu bằng sk-\";\n        break;\n      case \"GITLAB_TOKEN\":\n        message = \"GitLab Personal Access Token (https://gitlab.com → Settings → Access Tokens)\";\n        name = \"gitlabToken\";\n        validate = (v) => v.startsWith(\"glpat-\") || \"Phải bắt đầu bằng glpat-\";\n        break;\n      case \"CONF_TOKEN\":\n        questions.push({\n          type: \"input\",\n          name: \"confUrl\",\n          message: chalk.cyan(\"Confluence Base URL (VD: https://annoinfo.atlassian.net/wiki):\"),\n          default: \"https://annoinfo.atlassian.net/wiki\",\n          validate: (v) => v.startsWith(\"http\") || \"URL phải bắt đầu bằng http\"\n        });\n        questions.push({\n          type: \"input\",\n          name: \"confEmail\",\n          message: chalk.cyan(\"Confluence Email (email đăng nhập Atlassian):\"),\n          default: \"\",\n          validate: (v) => v.includes(\"@\") || \"Email không hợp lệ\"\n        });\n        questions.push({\n          type: \"input\",\n          name: \"confToken\",\n          message: chalk.cyan(\"Confluence API Token (https://id.atlassian.com → Security → API Tokens):\"),\n          default: \"\",\n          validate: (v) => v.length > 5 || \"Token không hợp lệ\"\n        });\n        continue;\n      case \"STITCH_API_KEY\":\n        message = \"Stitch API Key (https://stitch.design → Dashboard)\";\n        name = \"stitchKey\";\n        validate = (v) => v.length > 10 || \"Token không hợp lệ\";\n        break;\n      case \"TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN\":\n        message = \"Telegram Bot Token (từ @BotFather, format: 123456:ABC-DEF...)\";\n        name = \"telegramBot\";\n        validate = (v) => v.includes(\":\") || \"Bot token phải có dạng xxx:yyy\";\n        break;\n    }\n\n    questions.push({\n      type: \"input\",\n      name,\n      message: chalk.cyan(`${cred}:`),\n      default: \"\",\n      validate\n    });\n  }\n\n  const pathQuestions = [\n    {\n      type: \"input\",\n      name: \"openclawPath\",\n      message: chalk.cyan(\"openclaw home (ENTER = ~/.openclaw):\"),\n      default: \"$HOME/.openclaw\",\n      validate: (v) => v.length > 0 || \"Path không được trống\"\n    }\n  ];\n  return inquirer.prompt([...questions, ...pathQuestions]);\n}\n\n// ─── Inject credentials into config ────────────────────────────────────\nfunction applyCredentials(config, answers, team) {\n  // AHV API Key\n  config.env.AHVHOLDING_API_KEY = answers.ahvApiKey;\n  config.models.providers.ahvholding.apiKey = answers.ahvApiKey;\n\n  // GitLab Token\n  if (answers.gitlabToken) {\n    config.env.GITLAB_TOKEN = answers.gitlabToken;\n    const gitlab = config.mcp?.servers?.gitlab;\n    if (gitlab?.env) {\n      gitlab.env.GITLAB_URL = answers.gitlabUrl || 'https://gitlab.com';\n      gitlab.env.GITLAB_TOKEN = answers.gitlabToken;\n    }\n  }\n\n  // Confluence — mcp.servers (NOT mcpServers)\n  const mcpServers = config.mcp?.servers || {};\n  for (const key of Object.keys(mcpServers)) {\n    if (key === \"confluence\" && mcpServers[key].env) {\n      mcpServers[key].env.CONFLUENCE_API_TOKEN = answers.confToken;\n    }\n    if (key === \"stitch\" && mcpServers[key].env && answers.stitchKey) {\n      mcpServers[key].env.STITCH_API_KEY = answers.stitchKey;\n    }\n  }\n\n  // Telegram Bot — channels.telegram.bots (NOT accounts)\n  const botKeys = Object.keys(config.channels?.telegram?.bots || {});\n  for (const botKey of botKeys) {\n    if (config.channels.telegram.bots[botKey].botToken === \"YOUR_TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN\") {\n      config.channels.telegram.bots[botKey].botToken = answers.telegramBot;\n    }\n  }\n\n  return config;\n}\n\n// ─── Apply config to ~/.openclaw ────────────────────────────────────────\nfunction applyConfig(config, answers, team) {\n  const openclawPath = getOpenclawPath(answers.openclawPath);\n  const openclawDir = path.dirname(openclawPath);\n  const workspaceDir = getWorkspacePath(answers.openclawPath);\n\n  console.log(chalk.dim(\"\\n📁 Tạo thư mục...\\n\"));\n\n  // Create directories\n  const dirs = [openclawDir, workspaceDir];\n  for (const dir of dirs) {\n    if (!fs.existsSync(dir)) {\n      fs.mkdirSync(dir, { recursive: true });\n      console.log(`  ${chalk.green(\"📂\")} Tạo: ${dir}`);\n    }\n  }\n\n  // Backup existing config\n  if (fs.existsSync(openclawPath)) {\n    const backupPath = openclawPath + `.backup-${Date.now()}.json`;\n    fs.copyFileSync(openclawPath, backupPath);\n    console.log(`  ${chalk.yellow(\"💾\")} Backup: ${backupPath}`);\n  }\n\n  // Apply path substitutions using answers.openclawPath\n  const homePath = answers.openclawPath\n    ? answers.openclawPath.replace(/^\\$HOME/, process.env.HOME || \"\")\n    : (process.env.HOME || \"\") + \"/.openclaw\";\n\n  // Build final config from template (config already has credentials injected)\n  let finalConfig = JSON.parse(JSON.stringify(config));\n\n  // Fix default workspace\n  if (finalConfig.agents?.defaults?.workspace) {\n    finalConfig.agents.defaults.workspace = `${homePath}/workspace`;\n  }\n  // Fix per-agent workspaces and agentDirs\n  for (const agent of finalConfig.agents?.list || []) {\n    if (agent.workspace?.startsWith(\"/path/to/\")) {\n      agent.workspace = `${homePath}/workspaces/${agent.id}`;\n    }\n    if (agent.agentDir?.startsWith(\"/path/to/\")) {\n      agent.agentDir = `${homePath}/agents/${agent.id}/agent`;\n    }\n  }\n  // Fix MCP server paths — use mcp.servers\n  const mcpServers = finalConfig.mcp?.servers || {};\n  for (const key of Object.keys(mcpServers)) {\n    const srv = mcpServers[key];\n    if (srv.command === \"node\" && srv.args) {\n      for (let i = 0; i < srv.args.length; i++) {\n        if (srv.args[i].startsWith(\"/path/to/\")) {\n          srv.args[i] = `${homePath}/mcp-stitch-key/server.mjs`;\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n\n  fs.writeFileSync(openclawPath, JSON.stringify(finalConfig, null, 2), \"utf8\");\n  console.log(`  ${chalk.green(\"✅\")} Paths substituted: ${homePath}`);\n\n  // ─── Unpack encrypted skills ─────────────────────────────────────────────\n  // Skills go to ~/.openclaw/skills/{agent}/SKILL.md\n  const packPath = path.join(__dirname, \"..\", \"skills.pack\");\n  if (fs.existsSync(packPath)) {\n    unpackSkills(packPath, homePath);\n  } else {\n    console.log(chalk.yellow(`  ⚠️  skills.pack not found — skills skipped`));\n  }\n\n  // ─── Init agents (workspace + files) ─────────────────────────────────────────\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`\\n  🤖 Tạo ${TEAMS[team].agents.length} agent workspaces...\\n`));\n  for (const agentId of TEAMS[team].agents) {\n    const wsDir = path.join(homePath, \"workspaces\", agentId);\n    fs.mkdirSync(wsDir, { recursive: true });\n\n    const nameMap = {\n      \"senior-backend\":\"Senior Backend Engineer\",\"senior-frontend\":\"Senior Frontend Engineer\",\n      \"senior-architect\":\"Senior System Architect\",\"senior-devops\":\"Senior DevOps Engineer\",\n      \"senior-qa\":\"Senior QA Engineer\",\"senior-security\":\"Senior Security Engineer\",\n      \"typescript-reviewer\":\"TypeScript Reviewer\",\"shadcn-expert\":\"shadcn/ui Expert\",\n      \"clean-code\":\"Clean Code Specialist\",\"coding-standards\":\"Coding Standards Enforcer\",\n      \"refactor-cleaner\":\"Refactor Cleaner\",\"realistic-seeder\":\"Realistic Seeder\",\n      \"planner\":\"Planner Agent\",\"prompt-optimizer\":\"Prompt Optimizer\",\n      \"agile-product-owner\":\"Agile Product Owner\",\"product-strategy\":\"Product Strategist\",\n      \"market-intelligence\":\"Market Intelligence Agent\",\"content-strategy\":\"Content Strategist\",\n      \"product-marketing-context\":\"Product Marketing Agent\",\"epic-design\":\"Epic Designer\",\n      \"playwright-pro\":\"Playwright Pro\",\"code-reviewer\":\"Code Reviewer\",\n      \"security-reviewer\":\"Security Reviewer\",\"performance-optimizer\":\"Performance Optimizer\"\n    };\n    const displayName = nameMap[agentId] || agentId;\n\n    // Copy agent files from existing OpenClaw workspace on this machine\n    // Try multiple common locations\n    const searchPaths = [\n      path.join(process.env.OPENCLAW_HOME || \"\", \"workspaces2\", \"v4-ecosystem-review\", agentId),\n      path.join(process.env.HOME || \"\", \".openclaw\", \"workspaces2\", \"v4-ecosystem-review\", agentId),\n      path.join(process.env.HOME || \"\", \".openclaw\", \"workspaces\", agentId),\n    ];\n    const coreFiles = [\"SOUL.md\",\"IDENTITY.md\",\"AGENTS.md\",\"USER.md\",\n      \"BOOTSTRAP.md\",\"HEARTBEAT.md\",\"TOOLS.md\",\"MEMORY.md\",\n      \"SKILL_GATES.md\",\"DEV_GATE.md\"];\n\n    let copied = 0;\n    for (const srcDir of searchPaths) {\n      if (fs.existsSync(srcDir)) {\n        for (const file of coreFiles) {\n          const src = path.join(srcDir, file);\n          if (fs.existsSync(src)) {\n            fs.copyFileSync(src, path.join(wsDir, file));\n            copied++;\n          }\n        }\n        break; // stop at first found\n      }\n    }\n    if (copied === 0) {\n      console.log(chalk.yellow(`  ⚠️  No source agent files found for ${agentId} — skipping`));\n    }\n    console.log(chalk.dim(`  ✅ ${agentId}`));\n  }\n\n  return openclawPath;\n}\n\n// ─── Restart gateway ───────────────────────────────────────────────────\nfunction restartGateway() {\n  console.log(chalk.dim(\"\\n🔄 Restarting OpenClaw gateway...\\n\"));\n  try {\n    execSync(\"openclaw gateway restart\", { encoding: \"utf8\", timeout: 30000 });\n    console.log(`  ${chalk.green(\"✅\")} Gateway restarted`);\n  } catch (e) {\n    console.log(chalk.yellow(\"  ⚠️  Không restart được tự động. Chạy thủ công:\"));\n    console.log(chalk.cyan(\"    openclaw gateway restart\"));\n  }\n}\n\n// ─── Main ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nasync function main() {\n  console.log(BANNER);\n\n  // Parse args\n  const args = process.argv.slice(2);\n  let teamArg = null;\n  let skipIntro = false;\n\n  for (const arg of args) {\n    if (arg === \"--team\" || arg === \"-t\") {\n      const idx = args.indexOf(arg);\n      teamArg = args[idx + 1];\n    }\n    if (arg.startsWith(\"--team=\")) {\n      teamArg = arg.replace(\"--team=\", \"\");\n    }\n    if (arg === \"--yes\" || arg === \"-y\") skipIntro = true;\n  }\n\n  // Check prereqs\n  checkPrereqs();\n\n  // Select team\n  let team = teamArg;\n  if (!team) {\n    const { selected } = await inquirer.prompt([\n      {\n        type: \"list\",\n        name: \"selected\",\n        message: chalk.cyan(\"Chọn team của bạn:\"),\n        choices: [\n          { name: \"👨💻 Team Dev  — Backend, Frontend, DevOps, Architecture\", value: \"dev\" },\n          { name: \"📊 Team BA   — Product Owner, Strategy, Epic Design\", value: \"ba\" },\n          { name: \"🧪 Team QA  — QA, Playwright, Security, Performance\", value: \"qa\" }\n        ]\n      }\n    ]);\n    team = selected;\n  }\n\n  if (!TEAMS[team]) {\n    console.log(chalk.red(`\\n❌ Team không hợp lệ: ${team}`));\n    console.log(chalk.dim(\"Chọn: dev | ba | qa\\n\"));\n    process.exit(1);\n  }\n\n  console.log(chalk.bold(`\\n${chalk.cyan(\"▶\")} ${TEAMS[team].name}`));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`   ${TEAMS[team].desc}`));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`   Agents: ${TEAMS[team].agents.length}`));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`   MCP: ${TEAMS[team].mcp.join(\", \")}\\n`));\n\n  // Confirm\n  if (!skipIntro) {\n    const { confirm } = await inquirer.prompt([\n      {\n        type: \"confirm\",\n        name: \"confirm\",\n        message: chalk.cyan(\"Tiếp tục cài đặt?\"),\n        default: true\n      }\n    ]);\n    if (!confirm) {\n      console.log(chalk.dim(\"\\nĐã hủy.\\n\"));\n      process.exit(0);\n    }\n  }\n\n  // Load template\n  console.log(chalk.dim(\"📋 Load config template...\\n\"));\n  let config = loadTemplate(team);\n\n  // Collect credentials\n  console.log(chalk.bold(chalk.underline(\"\\n🔐 Nhập credentials (tự tạo cho team của bạn)\\n\")));\n  const answers = await collectCredentials(team);\n\n  // Apply\n  config = applyCredentials(config, answers, team);\n\n  // Summary\n  console.log(chalk.bold(\"\\n📦 Tổng kết config:\\n\"));\n  console.log(`  ${chalk.green(\"✓\")} Team: ${TEAMS[team].name}`);\n  console.log(`  ${chalk.green(\"✓\")} Agents: ${TEAMS[team].agents.join(\", \")}`);\n  console.log(`  ${chalk.green(\"✓\")} MCP: ${TEAMS[team].mcp.join(\", \")}`);\n\n  // Confirm before writing\n  const { write } = await inquirer.prompt([\n    {\n      type: \"confirm\",\n      name: \"write\",\n      message: chalk.cyan(\"\\nGhi config vào ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json?\"),\n      default: true\n    }\n  ]);\n\n  if (!write) {\n    console.log(chalk.dim(\"\\nĐã hủy. Config chưa được ghi.\\n\"));\n    process.exit(0);\n  }\n\n  const configPath = applyConfig(config, answers, team);\n  const homePath = answers.openclawPath\n    ? answers.openclawPath.replace(/^\\$HOME\\//, process.env.HOME || \"\")\n    : (process.env.HOME || \"\") + \"/.openclaw\";\n\n  // Restart gateway\n  restartGateway();\n\n  // Done\n  console.log(chalk.bold(chalk.green(\"\\n✅ Setup hoàn tất!\\n\")));\n  console.log(`  Config: ${configPath}`);\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`\\n  Đã làm:`));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`  • Credentials + config → ${configPath}`));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`  • Skills unpacked → ${homePath}/skills/`));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`  • ${TEAMS[team].agents.length} agent workspaces + files tạo`));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`  • Gateway restarted`));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`\\n  Kiểm tra: openclaw status`));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`  Xem agents: openclaw agents list`));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`  Gateway token: grep token ${configPath}`));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`  TUI: openclaw tui --token <token>`));\n\n}\n\nmain().catch((err) => {\n  console.error(chalk.red(\"\\n❌ Lỗi:\"), err.message);\n  process.exit(1);\n});","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776255864595}}
{"type":"message","id":"2f657e96","parentId":"72894118","timestamp":"2026-04-15T12:24:40.151Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I found the bug! Let me look at the `applyCredentials` function carefully:\n\n```javascript\nfunction applyCredentials(config, answers, team) {\n  // ...\n  // Confluence — mcp.servers (NOT mcpServers)\n  const mcpServers = config.mcp?.servers || {};\n  for (const key of Object.keys(mcpServers)) {\n    if (key === \"confluence\" && mcpServers[key].env) {\n      mcpServers[key].env.CONFLUENCE_API_TOKEN = answers.confToken;  // Only sets CONFLUENCE_API_TOKEN!\n\n\n```\n\nThe issue is that the `collectCredentials` function only captures `confUrl`, `confEmail`, and `confToken` separately, but `applyCredentials` is mapping them to the wrong environment variable names—it's setting `CONF_BASE_URL` and `CONF_USERNAME` instead of what the config template actually expects.\n\nLooking at the current `openclaw.json`, I can see the correct variable names are already being used there, but the script is applying the wrong ones. Let me trace through the credentials collection flow to find where this mismatch is happening.\n\n```\n\njson\n\"CONF_USERNAME\": \"ninhkhuongpl7@gmail.com\",\n\"CONF_TOKEN\": \"...\"\n```\n\nThe `applyCredentials` function is mapping the collected answers to `CONFLUENCE_BASE_URL`, `CONFLUENCE_EMAIL`, and `CONFLUENCE_API_TOKEN`, but the actual openclaw.json uses different variable names like `CONF_BASE_URL`, `CONF_USERNAME`, and `CONF_TOKEN`. This means even though the credentials are being collected and injected into the config object, they're being stored under the wrong keys, so the MCP server won't actually use them. I'm seeing the disconnect now—the template config uses different environment variable names than what the script is setting. The script tries to inject `CONFLUENCE_API_TOKEN`, but the actual openclaw.json is looking for `CONF_USERNAME` and `CONF_TOKEN`, which is why the credentials aren't being picked up even though the script ran without errors. The issue is that `applyCredentials` is setting `CONFLUENCE_API_TOKEN` but the MCP server expects `CONF_TOKEN`, and it's also not setting `CONF_USERNAME` at all. The email field is being collected as `confEmail` but never actually applied to the config, so I need to map `confUrl` to `CONF_BASE_URL`, `confEmail` to `CONF_USERNAME`, and `confToken` to `CONF_TOKEN` instead.","thinkingSignature":"f3dc3c5f337c4b06f39f2c591b9d722443bbfa569ca3cc9fa27ba73d48f4d3f6"},{"type":"text","text":"Tìm ra bug rồi. Vấn đề nằm trong function `applyCredentials` của setup script. Tôi phân tích:\n\n**Root cause:** Script `collectCredentials` thu thập 3 trường Confluence (`confUrl`, `confEmail`, `confToken`) nhưng `applyCredentials` chỉ set `CONFLUENCE_API_TOKEN` (sai tên biến) và **KHÔNG set `CONF_USERNAME` / `CONF_EMAIL`**. Kết quả: credentials không được apply đúng vào MCP server config.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ju8skhqwp0sz_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup/bin/ahv-setup.js","offset":155,"limit":25}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":5606,"output":717,"cacheRead":26556,"cacheWrite":2496,"totalTokens":35375,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776255864648,"responseId":"062eb679b0035034171777cbd3dfd5af"}}
