{"type":"message","id":"f7d31357","parentId":"3772fd30","timestamp":"2026-04-15T12:33:38.291Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Everything looks good. Let me give Lead a clear status report.\n\nThe 3 bugs were:\n1. Confluence credentials only set CONF_TOKEN (missing CONF_BASE_URL + CONF_USERNAME) → FIXED\n2. install.sh didn't handle piped mode → FIXED  \n3. team select prompt blocked in piped mode → FIXED\n\nBoth files are committed to main.","thinkingSignature":"d8ac915530b920343fc1acc0c05d30a2a7731096fdcf16d9b3db0d97992e7b1f"},{"type":"text","text":"**Cả 3 bug đã được fix và commit.** Tóm tắt trạng thái:\n\n| Bug | Trạng thái |\n|-----|-----------|\n| Confluence: chỉ set `CONF_TOKEN`, bỏ `CONF_USERNAME` + `CONF_BASE_URL` | ✅ Đã fix |\n| `curl \\| bash` treo ở prompt y/n | ✅ Đã fix |\n| Team selection prompt block pipe mode | ✅ Đã fix |\n\n**Files đã commit:**\n- `ahv-openclaw-setup/bin/ahv-setup.js`\n- `ahv-openclaw-setup/install.sh` (new file)\n\n**Kiểm tra:**\n- ✅ `node --check` pass\n- ✅ `install.sh` tồn tại và có `skipFlag` logic\n- ✅ Template configs đúng env var names (`CONF_BASE_URL`, `CONF_USERNAME`, `CONF_TOKEN`)\n- ✅ `applyCredentials` apply đủ 3 trường vào mọi confluence MCP server\n- ✅ Pipe mode tự detect → `--yes` → team default `dev`\n\nBây giờ user mới chạy `curl ... | bash` sẽ hoạt động bình thường, không treo ở prompt."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":284,"output":349,"cacheRead":68451,"cacheWrite":354,"totalTokens":69438,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776256409383,"responseId":"062eb89a795b4e06341e40f297cee0f0"}}
