{"type":"message","id":"895adea4","parentId":"00748066","timestamp":"2026-04-15T12:52:13.493Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the FULL picture:\n\nThe setup repo (`ahv-openclaw-setup/`) has a VERY different OpenClaw config schema than what I'm using in the workspace (`v4-ecosystem-review/`). The setup repo uses an OLDER/LIGHTER config format:\n- `mcp.servers` (nested) instead of `mcpServers` (top-level)\n- No `accounts`, `auth`, `browser`, `session`, `skills`, `tools` sections\n- Different overall structure\n\nThe local configs in `ahv-openclaw-setup/configs/` were copied FROM the workspace (v4-ecosystem-review) when I ran `cp` earlier. \n\nSo the local files are actually corrupted—they have the workspace schema with `mcpServers` but they're sitting in the setup repo where the script expects the older format with `mcp.servers`. The original committed files in the setup repo are correct, and my changes actually broke them. The script handles this mismatch by checking for both `mcpServers` and `mcp.servers` depending on which config version it's dealing with.\n\nNow I need to restore the committed versions of the config files since they have the proper `mcp.servers` format that matches what the setup script actually generates.","thinkingSignature":"15dd7b3e37c6810835da69d1a5d9efa922f651c50d783918d01e566df38cf2a7"},{"type":"text","text":"Hiểu rồi! Configs local bị ghi đè từ workspace (sai schema). Setup repo dùng `mcp.servers`, không phải `mcpServers`. Restore về đúng:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jyncdd22f0ie_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup && git checkout HEAD -- configs/ && python3 -c \"\nimport json\nfor f in ['configs/team-dev.json', 'configs/team-ba.json', 'configs/team-qa.json']:\n    d = json.load(open(f))\n    print(f, 'mcp.servers:', list(d.get('mcp',{}).get('servers',{}).keys()) if 'mcp' in d else 'N/A')\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":244,"output":445,"cacheRead":163645,"cacheWrite":665,"totalTokens":164999,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776257522283,"responseId":"062ebcf39f5b2b8516ad9e937bab0fc4"}}
