{"type":"message","id":"f0596aba","parentId":"de978f47","timestamp":"2026-04-16T03:06:19.152Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me also fix the REQUIRED_CREDS to match the env vars we're actually using in the config. The current setup uses:\n- `AHV_API_KEY` → but the config uses `${AHVHOLDING_API_KEY}`\n- `GITLAB_TOKEN` → matches\n- `CONF_TOKEN` → the config uses `CONFLUENCE_BASE_URL`, `CONFLUENCE_USERNAME`, `CONFLUENCE_TOKEN`\n- `STITCH_API_KEY` → matches\n- `TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN` → matches\n\nI need to update `buildAnswersFromEnv` and `collectCredentials` to match the actual env var names used in the config:\n\n\n- `AHVHOLDING_API_KEY` for the AHV API key\n- `GITLAB_TOKEN` and `GITLAB_URL` for GitLab\n- `CONFLUENCE_BASE_URL`, `CONFLUENCE_USERNAME`, `CONFLUENCE_TOKEN` for Confluence credentials\n- `STITCH_API_KEY` for Stitch\n- `TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN` for Telegram\n\nNow I'm going to update the applyConfig function to write to a generated file instead.","thinkingSignature":"e9b1b1a17053004561628703c86146cd59397d59e25d1e7ba6e290c5f08ce42c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qawlcsk8l0kb_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup && python3 << 'PYEOF'\nwith open('bin/ahv-setup.js', 'r') as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\n# Fix 1: applyConfig - write to generated-{team}.json instead of openclaw.json\nold_apply = '''function applyConfig(config, answers, team) {\n  const openclawPath = getOpenclawPath(answers.openclawPath);\n  const homePath = (answers.openclawPath || \"$HOME/.openclaw\").replace(/^\\\\$HOME/, process.env.HOME || \"\");\n\n  // Ensure directories exist\n  fs.mkdirSync(path.dirname(openclawPath), { recursive: true });\n  fs.mkdirSync(path.join(homePath, \"workspaces\"), { recursive: true });\n\n  // Backup\n  if (fs.existsSync(openclawPath)) {\n    fs.copyFileSync(openclawPath, openclawPath + `.backup-${Date.now()}.json`);\n  }'''\n\nnew_apply = '''function applyConfig(config, answers, team) {\n  const homePath = (answers.openclawPath || \"$HOME/.openclaw\").replace(/^\\\\$HOME/, process.env.HOME || \"\");\n  // Write to a generated file — NEVER overwrite existing openclaw.json\n  const generatedPath = path.join(homePath, `openclaw.generated-${team}.json`);\n\n  // Ensure directories exist\n  fs.mkdirSync(path.dirname(generatedPath), { recursive: true });\n  fs.mkdirSync(path.join(homePath, \"workspaces\"), { recursive: true });'''\n\nif old_apply in content:\n    content = content.replace(old_apply, new_apply)\n    print('✅ applyConfig path fix')\nelse:\n    print('❌ applyConfig path not found')\n\n# Fix 2: Change write target from openclawPath to generatedPath\nold_write = 'fs.writeFileSync(openclawPath, JSON.stringify(finalConfig, null, 2), \"utf8\");\\n  console.log(`  ${chalk.green(\"✅\")} Config: ${openclawPath}`);'\nnew_write = 'fs.writeFileSync(generatedPath, JSON.stringify(finalConfig, null, 2), \"utf8\");\\n  console.log(`  ${chalk.green(\"✅\")} Config: ${generatedPath}`);'\n\nif old_write in content:\n    content = content.replace(old_write, new_write)\n    print('✅ write path fix')\nelse:\n    print('❌ write path not found')\n\n# Fix 3: Remove the write confirmation prompt (it's now a generated file, no need to confirm)\nold_confirm = '''  const { write } = await inquirer.prompt([{\n    type: \"confirm\", name: \"write\",\n    message: chalk.cyan(\"\\\\nGhi config vao ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json?\"), default: true\n  }]);\n  if (!write) { console.log(chalk.dim(\"\\\\nDa huy.\\\\n\")); process.exit(0); }\n\n  applyConfig(config, answers, team);'''\nnew_confirm = '''  applyConfig(config, answers, team);'''\n\nif old_confirm in content:\n    content = content.replace(old_confirm, new_confirm)\n    print('✅ removed write confirmation')\nelse:\n    print('❌ write confirmation not found')\n\n# Fix 4: Always skip restart (user will restart manually)\nold_restart = '  if (!skipIntro) restartGateway();'\nnew_restart = '  // Gateway restart is the user\\'s responsibility'\nif old_restart in content:\n    content = content.replace(old_restart, new_restart)\n    print('✅ restart skip')\nelse:\n    print('❌ restart skip not found')\n\n# Fix 5: Update summary message\nold_summary = '  console.log(`  ${chalk.green(\"✓\")} MCP: ${TEAMS[team].mcp.join(\", \")}`);'\nnew_summary = '  console.log(`  ${chalk.green(\"✓\")} MCP: ${TEAMS[team].mcp.join(\", \")}`);\\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`\\\\n  Config file: ${homePath}/openclaw.generated-${team}.json`));'\nif old_summary in content:\n    content = content.replace(old_summary, new_summary)\n    print('✅ summary update')\nelse:\n    print('❌ summary not found')\n\n# Fix 6: Update SUCCESS message\nold_success = '''  console.log(chalk.bold(chalk.green(\"\\\\n✅ Setup hoan tat!\\\\n\")));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`  • Config + workspaces: ${homePath}`));'''\nnew_success = '''  console.log(chalk.bold(chalk.green(\"\\\\n✅ Setup hoan tat!\\\\n\")));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`  • Generated config: ${homePath}/openclaw.generated-${team}.json`));\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`  • Workspaces: ${homePath}/workspaces/`));'''\nif old_success in content:\n    content = content.replace(old_success, new_success)\n    print('✅ success message update')\nelse:\n    print('❌ success message not found')\n\n# Fix 7: Update \"openclaw gateway restart\" reminder\nold_reminder = '  console.log(chalk.dim(`\\\\n  openclaw gateway restart`));'\nnew_reminder = '  console.log(chalk.dim(`\\\\n  IMPORTANT: Review ${homePath}/openclaw.generated-${team}.json`));\\n  console.log(chalk.dim(`  then merge into your openclaw.json or rename it.`));'\nif old_reminder in content:\n    content = content.replace(old_reminder, new_reminder)\n    print('✅ reminder update')\nelse:\n    print('❌ reminder not found')\n\nwith open('bin/ahv-setup.js', 'w') as f:\n    f.write(content)\nprint('Done.')\nPYEOF"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":266,"output":1498,"cacheRead":103005,"cacheWrite":978,"totalTokens":105747,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776308745357,"responseId":"062f850bb3b08a761c93c480cc0dba04"}}
