{"type":"message","id":"79710d48","parentId":"9b73e40a","timestamp":"2026-04-16T03:06:47.380Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see - the file uses literal emoji `✅` not unicode escapes. Let me check the actual content. Also the `skipIntro` check is around the write confirmation. I need to remove the whole block. But since the confirmation was supposed to be skipped in pipe mode (when `skipIntro=true`), it might actually be fine. Let me think about this...\n\nThe issue is: even in pipe mode (skipIntro=true), if there's a write confirmation that asks about overwriting openclaw.json, and we don't want it to overwrite, then we should just remove the confirmation entirely (since we're now writing to a generated file, not the real one).\n \nThe confirmation was checking whether to write to openclaw.json, but now we're writing to the generated file instead, so the whole check is unnecessary. I should remove the entire block.","thinkingSignature":"2f5af05bbfc378f4a5f531e764f8c5313bd6990b9c6cdce24f625dfb9aa12249"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tt8hoicnvi9h_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup && python3 << 'PYEOF'\nwith open('bin/ahv-setup.js', 'r') as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\n# The confirmation block - use the exact text from sed output\nold_block = '''  const homePath = (answers.openclawPath || \"$HOME/.openclaw\").replace(/^\\\\$HOME/, process.env.HOME || \"\");\n\n  if (!skipIntro) {\n    const { write } = await inquirer.prompt([{\n      type: \"confirm\", name: \"write\",\n      message: chalk.cyan(\"\\\\nGhi config vao ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json?\"), default: true\n    }]);\n    if (!write) { console.log(chalk.dim(\"\\\\nDa huy.\\\\n\")); process.exit(0);  }\n  }\n\n  applyConfig(config, answers, team);'''\n\nnew_block = '''  const homePath = (answers.openclawPath || \"$HOME/.openclaw\").replace(/^\\\\$HOME/, process.env.HOME || \"\");\n\n  applyConfig(config, answers, team);'''\n\nif old_block in content:\n    content = content.replace(old_block, new_block)\n    print('✅ confirmation block removed')\nelse:\n    print('❌ not found')\n    # Find it\n    idx = content.find('Ghi config vao')\n    if idx >= 0:\n        print(repr(content[idx-50:idx+200]))\n\nwith open('bin/ahv-setup.js', 'w') as f:\n    f.write(content)\nPYEOF"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":316,"output":531,"cacheRead":105669,"cacheWrite":382,"totalTokens":106898,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776308791873,"responseId":"062f853979953a8e6997abc16158ebd0"}}
