{"type":"message","id":"5949b67d","parentId":"7cde79ea","timestamp":"2026-04-16T03:12:07.294Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_yjmraidhxim3_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[0;36m  ▶ Kiểm tra prerequisites...[0m\n[2m  • Node.js: v22.22.2[0m\n[2m  • npm: 10.9.7[0m\n[0;32m  ✅ Prerequisites OK[0m\n[2m  • AHV API Key: sk-3d8ed...[0m\n[0;36m  ▶ Tai AHV OpenClaw Setup...[0m\n[2m  • Repo da co — pulling latest...[0m\n[0;32m  ✅ Repo ready: /root/.openclaw-setup[0m\n[0;36m  ▶ Cai dependencies...[0m\n[0;32m  ✅ Dependencies installed[0m\n[0;36m  ▶ Chay setup cho team: dev...[0m\n[2m  • Detected piped mode — auto-skipping prompts[0m\n\n╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\n║   AHV OpenClaw Setup — Full Stack v2.0         ║\n║   Agents + MCP servers + skills + config        ║\n╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\n\n\n🔍 Kiểm tra prerequisites...\n\n  ✅ Node.js: v22.22.2\n  ✅ npm: 10.9.7\n  ✅ OpenClaw CLI: OK\n\n▶ 👨💻 Team Dev — Backend, Frontend, DevOps, Architecture\n   Agents: 12 | MCP: gitlab, confluence, stitch\n\n\n❌ Loi: object is not iterable (cannot read property Symbol(Symbol.iterator))"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":9460,"aggregated":"[0;36m  ▶ Kiểm tra prerequisites...[0m\n[2m  • Node.js: v22.22.2[0m\n[2m  • npm: 10.9.7[0m\n[0;32m  ✅ Prerequisites OK[0m\n[2m  • AHV API Key: sk-3d8ed...[0m\n[0;36m  ▶ Tai AHV OpenClaw Setup...[0m\n[2m  • Repo da co — pulling latest...[0m\n[0;32m  ✅ Repo ready: /root/.openclaw-setup[0m\n[0;36m  ▶ Cai dependencies...[0m\n[0;32m  ✅ Dependencies installed[0m\n[0;36m  ▶ Chay setup cho team: dev...[0m\n[2m  • Detected piped mode — auto-skipping prompts[0m\n\n╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\n║   AHV OpenClaw Setup — Full Stack v2.0         ║\n║   Agents + MCP servers + skills + config        ║\n╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\n\n\n🔍 Kiểm tra prerequisites...\n\n  ✅ Node.js: v22.22.2\n  ✅ np