{"type":"message","id":"7d448de2","parentId":"c72084c3","timestamp":"2026-04-16T03:19:23.976Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The install.sh still has the OLD code (pull from main)! The commit I pushed to feat/full-setup-mcp didn't get pulled because:1. The clone step happened FIRST (before my latest commits were pushed)\n2. Then git pull origin feat/full-setup-mcp ran BUT the install.sh code was already the old version\n\nWait no - my latest install.sh has `git fetch origin feat/full-setup-mcp && git reset --hard origin/feat/full-setup-mcp`. But the local install.sh still shows `git pull origin main --quiet`. This means the hard reset didn't overwrite install.sh!\n\nOh! I think I understand now. The `git reset --hard` ran BUT the file /root/.openclaw-setup/install.sh was MODIFIED locally (maybe by the first run that exited with an error). \n\nSo `git reset --hard` wouldn't overwrite a dirty file! That's the issue - the first run probably modified install.sh or the .git directory had local changes. I need to add a `git checkout -- .` or `git clean -fd` to force overwrite local files.","thinkingSignature":"a985dc54d5d751603efc368fc19be9468cfa0acedb3afa20e926bec84d01c1be"},{"type":"text","text":"\nFound it — `git reset --hard` skips dirty local files. Fix:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gvj9dkpilasg_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup && python3 - << 'PYEOF'\nwith open('install.sh', 'rb') as f:\n    raw = f.read()\n\nold = b'''    cd \"$INSTALL_DIR\" && git fetch origin feat/full-setup-mcp && git reset --hard origin/feat/full-setup-mcp'''\n\nnew = b'''    cd \"$INSTALL_DIR\" && git fetch origin feat/full-setup-mcp && git checkout origin/feat/full-setup-mcp -- . && git reset --hard origin/feat/full-setup-mcp'''\n\nif old in raw:\n    raw = raw.replace(old, new)\n    print('✅ checkout+reset updated')\nelse:\n    print('❌ not found')\n\nwith open('install.sh', 'wb') as f:\n    f.write(raw)\nPYEOF"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":439,"cacheRead":40231,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40670,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776309552231,"responseId":"062f88318ee6c794373333b32d60c58c"}}
