{"type":"message","id":"1ddf319a","parentId":"eb3eeeb3","timestamp":"2026-04-16T03:47:55.642Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Created the Confluence page. Let me also push this as a markdown file in the setup repo for reference.","thinkingSignature":"36689e658bfc5986493dedb51c6335d35c4eceff6f583531a185ec873bf84242"},{"type":"text","text":"Tạo xong Confluence ✅\n\n**Page:** [Hướng Dẫn Lấy API Keys — AHV OpenClaw Setup](https://dtlx.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/OTLXPA1/pages/128090113)\n\nBao gồm:\n- `AHVHOLDING_API_KEY` — dashboard ahvchat.com\n- `TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN` — @BotFather\n- `GITLAB_TOKEN` + `GITLAB_URL` — GitLab Settings → Access Tokens\n- `CONFLUENCE_URL` + `CONFLUENCE_EMAIL` + `CONFLUENCE_TOKEN` — Atlassian id.atlassian.com\n- `STITCH_API_KEY` — stitch.design Dashboard\n\nCó sẵn block env vars template để copy-paste nhanh."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":248,"output":206,"cacheRead":55798,"cacheWrite":2412,"totalTokens":58664,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776311268755,"responseId":"062f8ee5249d27d60d528cafa203bda9"}}
