{"type":"message","id":"267260dc","parentId":"d26371d9","timestamp":"2026-04-17T11:50:54.855Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"File doesn't exist, create it.","thinkingSignature":"03827f88bb6472808c73956c1ddd22e620d6b03875d62f954a98f00d710b6cd0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0x18wl65sca5_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/2026-04-17.md","content":"# memory/2026-04-17.md — Orbis Daily Log\n\n## Setup-openclaw Finalization (2026-04-16 → 2026-04-17)\n\n### Team Configs — Final State\n\nAll 4 team configs generated from real `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` schema (read-only reference):\n- `configs/team-dev.json` — 12 agents (backend, frontend, devops, arch, db, qa, security, refactor, seeder, planner, optimizer, prompt-optimizer) + gitlab + confluence + stitch MCP\n- `configs/team-ba.json` — 7 agents (po, market-intelligence, product-strategy, content-strategy, ai-seo, epic-design, stitch-design) + confluence + stitch MCP\n- `configs/team-qa.json` — 6 agents (senior-qa, code-reviewer, playwright-pro, performance-optimizer, senior-security, security-reviewer) + gitlab + confluence MCP\n- `configs/team-all.json` — 34 agents + gitlab + confluence + stitch MCP\n\n### ahv-setup.js — Final Fixes\n\n- `applyCredentials()`: Config uses `{{VAR}}` mustache-style placeholders (NOT `${VAR}`). Env var mapping: `AHVHOLDING_API_KEY` → `{{AHVHOLDING_API_KEY}}`, `TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN` → `{{TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN}}`, `GITLAB_TOKEN` → `{{GITLAB_TOKEN}}`, `CONFLUENCE_URL` → `{{CONFLUENCE_URL}}`, `CONFLUENCE_EMAIL` → `{{CONFLUENCE_EMAIL}}`, `CONFLUENCE_TOKEN` → `{{CONFLUENCE_TOKEN}}`\n- `applyConfig()`: Writes to `~/.openclaw/openclaw.generated-{team}.json` — **NEVER overwrites openclaw.json** ✅\n- `buildAnswersFromEnv()`: Reads AHVHOLDING_API_KEY, GITLAB_TOKEN, TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN, CONFLUENCE_URL, CONFLUENCE_EMAIL, CONFLUENCE_TOKEN from env vars in pipe/non-TTY mode\n- `teamCfg.agents` is an OBJECT (keyed by agent id), not an array — filter by checking `Object.keys(teamCfg.agents)`\n- `openclaw-full.json` used as base config (exists in `configs/`)\n\n### install.sh — Final Fixes\n\n- Pulls from `feat/full-setup-mcp` branch (not `main`) to get latest code\n- SETUP_TEAM env var: `dev|ba|qa|all` (defaults to `dev` if skipIntro)\n- Done message points to `openclaw.generated-{team}.json` with merge instructions\n- `--yes` flag skips all prompts including restart\n\n### Repo & Git Status\n\n- Repo: `git@github.com:maiychrus25/setup-openclaw.git`\n- `feat/full-setup-mcp` force-pushed to `main` (override protected main)\n- Final main: `12d415d` — \"fix: skip restart on --yes, add merge instructions\"\n- Remote URL: `https://github.com/maiychrus25/setup-openclaw` (HTTPS for curl)\n\n### User Install Command\n\n```bash\ncurl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/maiychrus25/setup-openclaw/main/install.sh | \\\n  AHVHOLDING_API_KEY=xxx \\\n  GITLAB_TOKEN=xxx \\\n  TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=xxx \\\n  CONFLUENCE_URL=https://xxx.atlassian.net/wiki \\\n  CONFLUENCE_EMAIL=xxx \\\n  CONFLUENCE_TOKEN=xxx \\\n  STITCH_API_KEY=xxx \\\n  SETUP_TEAM=dev \\\n  bash\n```\n\n### Confluence Setup Guide\n\nCreated: [Hướng Dẫn Lấy API Keys — AHV OpenClaw Setup](https://dtlx.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/OTLXPA1/pages/128090113)\nCovers: AHVHOLDING_API_KEY, TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN, GITLAB_TOKEN, CONFLUENCE (URL+EMAIL+TOKEN), STITCH_API_KEY\n\n## System State (2026-04-17)\n\n- DTLX BE (PID 381379) — previously high CPU (91.9%) ⚠️ — monitor\n- Gateway: running ✅\n- All 4 team configs verified: team-dev ✅ team-ba ✅ team-qa ✅ team-all ✅\n- skills.pack: 526 entries, 1.4 MB, encryption working ✅\n\n## NO_ACTIVE_TASKS\n\nNo pending work. setup-openclaw package is complete and pushed.\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":76,"output":1054,"cacheRead":22858,"cacheWrite":295,"totalTokens":24283,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"c