{"type":"message","id":"347d8289","parentId":"eca15270","timestamp":"2026-04-17T14:31:03.726Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, now I understand the structure. Let me check the qlhv-fe layout and the dtlx-fe layout more carefully. The qlhv-fe is a Next.js app and the dtlx-fe is a Vite app. They have different tech stacks!\n\nQLHV FE: Next.js (src/app directory)\nDTLX FE: Vite (src directory with index.html)\n\nThese are different tech stacks! The QLHV FE uses Next.js with the App Router, while DTLX FE uses plain Vite + React.\n\nLet me check the layout structure of both to understand what \"layout\" means in this context.","thinkingSignature":"449f93e29325e3320a7e96719c33aac8dad4d4e32c866a0aa4fc7bef60ec1420"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_anqooutr1i8b_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe && \\\n  echo \"=== QLHV FE layout ===\" && \\\n  find src/app -name \"layout*\" 2>/dev/null | head -10 && \\\n  echo \"---\" && \\\n  ls src/app/ && echo \"---\" && \\\n  find src/app -name \"sidebar*\" -o -name \"navbar*\" -o -name \"header*\" 2>/dev/null | head -10 && \\\n  echo \"---\" && \\\n  cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-frontend && \\\n  echo \"=== DTLX FE layout ===\" && \\\n  find src -name \"layout*\" 2>/dev/null | head -10 && \\\n  echo \"---\" && \\\n  ls src/ && echo \"---\" && \\\n  find src -name \"sidebar*\" -o -name \"navbar*\" -o -name \"header*\" 2>/dev/null | head -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1310,"output":379,"cacheRead":76099,"cacheWrite":563,"totalTokens":78351,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776436247881,"responseId":"063177190a948e3c4ec798e86f63646a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f4a2aae2","parentId":"347d8289","timestamp":"2026-04-17T14:31:04.152Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_anqooutr1i8b_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== QLHV FE layout ===\nsrc/app/(auth)/layout.tsx\nsrc/app/layout.tsx\n---\n(auth)\napple-icon.tsx\ncourses\ndashboard\nexam-batches\nglobals.css\ngraduation-exam\nhelp\nicon.png\nicon.svg\nicon.tsx\nlayout.tsx\nnotifications\nopengraph-image.tsx\npage.tsx\npractice\nprofile\nprogress\nrobots.ts\nsat-hach\nschedules\nsettings\nsitemap.ts\nstudents\ntuition\n---\n---\n=== DTLX FE layout ===\nsrc/layouts\n---\nApp.jsx\napis\nassets\ncomponents\nconfigs\nconstants\nhooks\nindex.css\nlayouts\nmain.jsx\npages\nrouters\nstores\nutils\n---"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":249,"aggregated":"=== QLHV FE layout ===\nsrc/app/(auth)/layout.tsx\nsrc/app/layout.tsx\n---\n(auth)\napple-icon.tsx\ncourses\ndashboard\nexam-batches\nglobals.css\ngraduation-exam\nhelp\nicon.png\nicon.svg\nicon.tsx\nlayout.tsx\nnotifications\nopengraph-image.tsx\npage.tsx\npractice\nprofile\nprogress\nrobots.ts\nsat-hach\nschedules\nsettings\nsitemap.ts\nstudents\ntuition\n---\n---\n=== DTLX FE layout ===\nsrc/layouts\n---\nApp.jsx\napis\nassets\ncomponents\nconfigs\nconstants\nhooks\nindex.css\nlayouts\nmain.jsx\npages\nrouters\nstores\nutils\n---","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776436264083}}
