{"type":"message","id":"16e265f3","parentId":"fe078b8e","timestamp":"2026-04-17T14:32:34.810Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a complete picture. Let me summarize what I've learned:\n\n**QLHV FE Layout (Reference):**\n- Next.js App Router with `src/app/layout.tsx`\n- Uses `src/components/layout/Sidebar.tsx` with groups: Overview, Management, Training, Settings\n- Nav items: Dashboard, Students, Courses, Tuition, Practice, Schedules, Progress, Graduation Exam, Sat Hach\n- Beautiful collapsible sidebar with premium glassmorphism tooltips\n- Uses framer-motion animations\n- Modern design with indigo theme\n\n**DTLX FE Layout (Current):**\n- Vite + React (not Next.js)\n- Uses `src/layouts/AdminLayout.jsx` with `src/components/SideNav.jsx`\n\n\n- Menu items organized in `src/constants/menu.constant.jsx`\n- Features nested submenus like Sales Management, Student Management, Schedule Management, Exam Management, Teacher Management, and Expense Management\n- Relies on Ant Design components with a different visual theme and a logo from `/assets/images/logoPhucAn.png`\n\nThe tech stacks are fundamentally different—QLHV uses Next.js while DTLX uses Vite—so I'm realizing Lead wants me to redesign the layout itself, not just port it directly. The core structure should include a collapsible sidebar with navigation groups, header with user menu, and a main content area, plus a fresh logo and navigation updates to reflect DTLX-specific items.\n\nI'm ready to present the current state to Lead for review before moving forward.","thinkingSignature":"e3644dad7fd738dbd7602f4ff738680d3d00e0f53587a385919a21002256e18e"},{"type":"text","text":"Dạ Lead! Đã pull code và phân tích xong. Báo cáo:\n\n---\n\n## ✅ Code pulled — `feat/redo-layout` from `origin/develop`\n\n| Item | Info |\n|---|---|\n| Repo | `ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-frontend` (GitLab) |\n| Branch | `feat/redo-layout` ← tracking `origin/develop` |\n| Latest commit | `497c986` — ci: edit .gitlab-ci.yml |\n| Remote URL | ✅ Updated → `https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-frontend.git` |\n\n---\n\n## 📊 So sánh 2 project\n\n| | QLHV FE (ref) | DTLX FE (target) |\n|---|---|---|\n| **Tech** | Next.js (App Router) | Vite + React |\n| **Layout** | `src/components/layout/Sidebar.tsx` + `Layout.tsx` | `src/layouts/AdminLayout.jsx` + `src/components/SideNav.jsx` |\n| **Nav groups** | Overview, Quản lý, Đào tạo, Settings | Sales, Học viên, Lịch học, Lịch thi, Giáo viên, Chi phí, Người dùng, Hệ thống |\n| **Animation** | Framer Motion | Antd + CSS |\n| **Theme** | Indigo/Premium glassmorphism | Bootstrap-style |\n| **Logo** | QLHV Driving | `/assets/images/logoPhucAn.png` |\n\n---\n\n## 📋 Kế hoạch đề xuất\n\n**Cần Lead duyệt trước khi làm:**\n\n1. **Layout structure** — giữ nguyên `AdminLayout.jsx` + `SideNav.jsx` (Vite structure)\n2. **Sidebar design** — update UI theo phong cách QLHV (glassmorphism, collapsible, tooltips)\n3. **Nav items** — thay nav labels từ QLHV → DTLX (nhưng giữ nguyên href/routes DTLX)\n4. **Logo** — thay bằng logo DTLX (logo mới hay giữ `logoPhucAn.png`?)\n5. **Header** — update user menu, notifications theo DTLX context\n6. **Responsive** — mobile drawer như QLHV\n\n---\n\n**Chờ Lead review và approve kế hoạch trước khi implement.** Có điều chỉnh gì về kế hoạch không?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":3583,"output":884,"cacheRead":83923,"cacheWrite":253,"totalTokens":88643,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776436333277,"responseId":"0631776e6181732df5f108fa3efd169d"}}
