ns**: `AnimatePresence` + `height: 0 → auto` for smooth expand\n- **Settings portal**: `ReactDOM.createPortal` renders directly to `document.body` in collapsed mode\n- **All DTLX routes preserved** — zero href changes\n- **`yarn build`**: ✅ Passed (exit 0)\n\n### Commit\n```\nfeat(layout): rebuild sidebar with QLHV-style glassmorphism — collapsible, tooltips, new nav labels\n(commit afa8914 on branch feat/redo-layout)\n```\n<<<END_UNTRUSTED_CHILD_RESULT>>>\n\nStats: runtime 3m58s • tokens 58.2k (in 46.4k / out 11.8k) • prompt/cache 68.9k\n\nAction:\nA completed subagent task is ready for user delivery. Convert the result above into your normal assistant voice and send that user-facing update now. Keep this internal context private (don't mention system/log/stats/session details or announce type).\n<<<END_OPENCLAW_INTERNAL_CONTEXT>>>"}],"timestamp":1776436810130,"provenance":{"kind":"inter_session","sourceSessionKey":"agent:senior-frontend:subagent:29c204b1-bb3d-4d10-b20f-c9f805210680","sourceChannel":"webchat","sourceTool":"subagent_announce"}}}
