{"type":"message","id":"ca1ae363","parentId":"be272ab1","timestamp":"2026-04-17T14:45:37.011Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_tadek2oi05r8_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== Login page ===\nimport React from \"react\";\nimport { Form, Input, Button } from \"antd\";\nimport { useDispatch } from \"react-redux\";\nimport { useNavigate } from \"react-router-dom\";\nimport { EyeTwoTone, EyeInvisibleOutlined } from \"@ant-design/icons\";\nimport { login } from \"../../stores/slices/auth.slice\";\nimport { showToast } from \"../../components/toast/toast\";\nimport { getHighestRole, ROLE_HOME } from \"../../constants/role.constant\";\n\nconst LoginForm = () => {\n  const dispatch = useDispatch();\n  const navigate = useNavigate();\n  // const handleLogin = async (values) => {\n  //   try {\n  //     await dispatch(login(values)).unwrap();\n  //     navigate(\"/\");\n  //   } catch (error) {\n  //     showToast(\"error\", \"Thất bại!\", error);\n  //   }\n  // };\n\n  const handleLogin = async (values) => {\n    try {\n      const res = await dispatch(login(values)).unwrap();\n\n      const roles = res?.roles || [];\n      const highestRole = getHighestRole(roles);\n      const home = ROLE_HOME[highestRole] || \"/403\";\n\n      navigate(home, { replace: true });\n    } catch (error) {\n      showToast(\"error\", \"Thất bại!\", error);\n    }\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <div\n      className=\"row d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center\"\n      style={{\n        backgroundImage: \"url('/assets/images/bg-login.jpg')\",\n        backgroundRepeat: \"no-repeat\",\n        width: \"100vw\",\n        height: \"100vh\",\n        backgroundSize: \"cover\",\n      }}\n    >\n      <div className=\"col-lg-4\" style={{ marginTop: \"-40px\" }}>\n        <div\n          className=\"card\"\n          style={{ boxShadow: \"0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15)\", borderRadius: 12 }}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":70,"aggregated":"=== Login page ===\nimport React from \"react\";\nimport { Form, Input, Button } from \"antd\";\nimport { useDispatch } from \"react-redux\";\nimport { useNavigate } from \"react-router-dom\";\nimport { EyeTwoTone, EyeInvisibleOutlined } from \"@ant-design/icons\";\nimport { login } from \"../../stores/slices/auth.slice\";\nimport { showToast } from \"../../components/toast/toast\";\nimport { getHighestRole, ROLE_HOME } from \"../../constants/role.constant\";\n\nconst LoginForm = () => {\n  const dispatch = useDispatch();\n  const navigate = useNavigate();\n  // const handleLogin = async (values) => {\n  //   try {\n  //     await dispatch(login(values)).unwrap();\n  //     navigate(\"/\");\n  //   } catch (error) {\n  //     showToast(\"error\", \"Thất bại!\", error);\n  //   }\n  // };\n\n  const handleLogin = async (values) => {\n    try {\n      const res = await dispatch(login(values)).unwrap();\n\n      const roles = res?.roles || [];\n      const highestRole = getHighestRole(roles);\n      const home = ROLE_HOME[highestRole] || \"/403\";\n\n      navigate(home, { replace: true });\n    } catch (error) {\n      showToast(\"error\", \"Thất bại!\", error);\n    }\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <div\n      className=\"row d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center\"\n      style={{\n        backgroundImage: \"url('/assets/images/bg-login.jpg')\",\n        backgroundRepeat: \"no-repeat\",\n        width: \"100vw\",\n        height: \"100vh\",\n        backgroundSize: \"cover\",\n      }}\n    >\n      <div className=\"col-lg-4\" style={{ marginTop: \"-40px\" }}>\n        <div\n          className=\"card\"\n          style={{ boxShadow: \"0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15)\", borderRadius: 12 }}","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776437136953}}
{"type":"message","id":"fba56c6d","parentId":"ca1ae363","timestamp":"2026-04-17T14:45:49.747Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The login page is the OLD version. The `55f75b7 perf: redesign and optimize login UI` commit is in the git history, but the working tree doesn't reflect those changes. This is because the agent checked out `origin/develop` and committed on top, but `origin/develop` at the time of checkout was at `497c986` — which doesn't include `55f75b7`.\n\nWait, but the `git log --oneline` showed `55f75b7` in the history of the current branch... Let me re-examine.\n\nActually, looking again at the log output:\n```\nafa8914  feat(layout): rebuild sidebar (AGENT COMMIT)\n\n\n497c986  ci: edit .gitlab-ci.yml\neb3da1b  Merge branch 'perf/redesign-login-ui' into 'develop'\n0b33285  chore: not commit .beads source this is only for dev\n8b99d62  ci: modify gitlab-ci.yaml for resolve...\n17ef980   Merge branch 'perf/redesign-login-ui' into 'develop'\ncc955ce  bd init: initialize beads issue tracking\nc9936e3  ci: modify gitlab ci not cache node_modules/\n55f75b7  perf: redesign and optimize login UI\n```\n\nSo the merge commit `eb3da1b` brought in the login UI redesign from `perf/redesign-login-ui`, and then `55f75b7` continued that work — meaning the login changes are definitely in the history. The issue is that when I checked out `origin/develop`, it was at `497c986`, which is after those merges, so the login redesign should be there. But the working tree shows the old version, which means either the checkout didn't actually get those files, or something overwrote them after checkout.\n\nLet me verify what's actually in the working tree right now versus what should be there according to the commit.","thinkingSignature":"0a3d0a31886978580de04a44bac33fa497df913ccb3bd23331f11b29fe73a3cf"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dsusi16l7z9g_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-tra