{"type":"message","id":"f6a12c2f","parentId":"55f5490e","timestamp":"2026-04-17T14:46:05.185Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The current `Login.jsx` has 108 lines but the redesigned version at `55f75b7` has 387 lines. The current working tree has the OLD login page, not the new redesigned one. This means the `origin/develop` that was checked out didn't include the `55f75b7` changes.\n\nBut the git log showed `55f75b7` in the history... Wait, this is very confusing. Let me think again.\n\nActually, looking at the git reflog output earlier:\n```\n5b86a7c HEAD@{2}: reset: moving to HEAD\n5b86a7c HEAD@{3}: commit: memory: log 2026-04-11...\n\n\n```\n\nThe workspace originally had a different repo (`maiychrus25/my-setup-openclaw.git`) at `5b86a7c`, which was then reset to HEAD and became the old DTLX frontend repo. When `feat/redo-layout` was created from `origin/develop`, it pulled from the DTLX GitLab repo at commit `497c986`. The commits `55f75b7` through `c9936e3` that appear in the git log are actually from this new DTLX repo's history, not remnants from the previous repository.\n\nSo the timeline is: the workspace started with the setup repo, then got converted to the DTLX frontend repo where `origin/develop` was checked out at `497c986`. The subsequent commits in the history—`17ef980`, `cc955ce`, `c9936e3`, `55f75b7`—are part of the DTLX repo's actual commit history, not foreign commits mixed in. I need to figure out how a commit from the DTLX repo's history ended up in the workspace's history when the workspace originally had a completely different repository.\n\n```\nI'm realizing the stash operation earlier might have pulled in commits from the bootstrap backup workspace's git history, which could explain how these commits appeared in the local git history even though the current working tree only reflects the DTLX repo at commit 497c986.\n``` The stash might have been from a different working tree entirely, so I should verify whether those older commits like `55f75b7` actually exist in the current repository's history or if they're bleeding in from somewhere else. Let me run a more direct check to see what's actually in this repo's commit graph.","thinkingSignature":"46e4891d99fbc1a974581532f42cfc35919cba5a3cdce6e533d1fd15750594ec"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9pw8zs3uwrmw_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-frontend && \\\n  echo \"=== Is 55f75b7 in this repo's objects? ===\" && git cat-file -t 55f75b7 2>/dev/null && \\\n  echo \"---\" && \\\n  echo \"=== Git rev-list (all commits) ===\" && git rev-list --all --oneline | head -20 && \\\n  echo \"---\" && \\\n  echo \"=== origin/develop ===\" && git rev-parse origin/develop && \\\n  echo \"---\" && \\\n  echo \"=== 55f75b7 ===\" && git rev-parse 55f75b7 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":370,"output":683,"cacheRead":97964,"cacheWrite":1119,"totalTokens":100136,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776437150043,"responseId":"06317a9f6b3e4631b374c3d5ffa51329"}}
